1. d4 d6 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. g3 g6 4. Bg2 Bg7 5. O-O O-O 6. a4 Nc6 7. a5 a6 ({Black's options are: a)} 7... Bf5 $6 8. a6 bxa6 9. Nh4 (9. c3 Qd7 (9... Bxb1 $6 10. Rxb1 Rb8 11. d5 Na5 12. Nd4 c5 13. dxc6 e5 14. Nc2 $16 {Arsovic,G-Ilincic,Z/Ulcinj 1997}) 10. Qa4 $14) 9... Be4 10. f3 Bd5 11. e4 (11. Rxa6 $6 Nb4 12. Ra4 Qb8 13. e4 Bc6 14. Ra3 Bb5 $13 {Mikhalchishin,A-Weindl,A/Bern 1996}) 11... Bc4 12. Re1 $16) ({b)} 7... Rb8 8. d5 Nb4 9. c4 $1 (9. c3 Na6 10. Be3 Ra8 11. Nd4 Bd7 $13 {Kengis,E-Neidhardt,C/Germany 1993}) 9... c5 10. Nc3 b6 11. axb6 Qxb6 12. e4 Ba6 13. Qe2 Nd7 14. Bf4 $14 {Gelashvili,T-Zulfugarli,M/Batumi 1999}) ({c)} 7... Bd7 8. c3 Qc8 9. Re1 a6 10. Nbd2 Bh3 11. e4 Bxg2 12. Kxg2 Nd7 13. Nc4 e5 14. dxe5 Ndxe5 15. Nfxe5 dxe5 16. Ne3 f5 17. Nd5 Kh8 18. f3 $14 {Gutman,L-Urban,H/Germany 1999}) ({d)} 7... d5 $5 8. Bf4 (8. Nbd2 Bf5 9. Nb3 Qc8 10. Ne5 Nb4 11. c3 Na6 12. Re1 Rd8 13. Be3 Ne4 14. Nd3 c6 $11 {Romanishin,O-Jobava,B/Leon 2001}) 8... Bf5 9. Ne5 Nxe5 10. Bxe5 Qd7 11. Nc3 c6 12. Na4 Qc8 13. Ra3 Bh3 14. Qc1 Bxg2 15. Kxg2 Ne4 16. Bxg7 Kxg7 17. Qf4 Qb8 18. Rfa1 Qxf4 19. gxf4 Rab8 20. Nc5 Nxc5 21. dxc5 $14 {Armbruster,A-Van der Weide,K/Senden 2000}) 8. d5 Nb8 ({Black can consider} 8... Ne5 9. Nxe5 dxe5 10. c4 e6 11. e4 exd5 12. exd5 Nd7 13. Nc3 f5 14. f3 h5 15. Be3 Qe7 16. Qb3 $14 {Cramling,P-Gullaksen,E/Catalan Bay 2003}) 9. c4 e6 (9... Nbd7 {did not prove a success:} 10. Nd4 Re8 11. e4 e5 12. Ne2 Rb8 13. Nec3 b6 14. axb6 cxb6 15. b4 Qc7 16. Na3 $16 Bb7 17. Be3 b5 18. Rc1 bxc4 19. Na4 Qd8 20. Nxc4 Qe7 21. Na5 Ba8 22. Rc4 Rec8 23. Qe2 Rxc4 24. Qxc4 Ne8 25. Rc1 f5 $2 26. Nc6 {1-0 Cramling,P-Tegzes,L/Richmond 2004}) 10. Nc3 Re8 ({Possible is} 10... exd5 11. cxd5 Re8 12. Bg5 Nbd7 13. Qc1 Nc5 14. Ra3 Bd7 15. Nd2 $14 b6 $2 16. b4 Nb7 17. Nce4 h6 18. Nxf6+ Bxf6 19. Bxf6 Qxf6 20. Qxc7 {1-0 Makarov,M-Loskutov,O/Tomsk 1998}) 11. Nd4 e5 12. Nc2 e4 $6 ({This is too risky, as the black e-pawn will soon become a target.} 12... Nbd7 $14 {is preferable}) 13. Ne3 Nbd7 14. Qc2 Qe7 15. Bd2 h5 16. Rac1 h4 17. b4 hxg3 18. hxg3 Qe5 19. Rfe1 Bf8 20. Nf1 $1 Qf5 21. Be3 Bg7 22. Red1 $1 Ne5 ({Or} 22... Nf8 23. Bd4 N8h7 24. Ne3 $16) 23. Nxe4 Nxe4 24. Qxe4 Qh5 25. f3 g5 26. g4 Qh4 27. Bf2 Qh6 28. Ng3 Bd7 29. Nf5 Qh7 30. Qc2 Ng6 31. Nxg7 Qxg7 32. Bd4 Qh6 33. e3 $16 Ne5 34. Qf2 Qg6 35. Rc3 Re7 36. e4 f6 37. c5 Bb5 38. cxd6 cxd6 39. Bf1 Kf7 40. Rdc1 Rh8 41. Bxb5 axb5 42. Bxe5 fxe5 43. Rc8 $2 ({A blunder. Not that difficult was} 43. Rc7 Qh6 44. Qb6 $1 $18) 43... Rh3 $1 44. Kf1 Qh6 45. Qe3 $1 Rh2 46. R8c2 $1 Kg6 47. Ke1 Rh7 (47... Rxc2 48. Rxc2 Qh1+ 49. Ke2 Qb1 50. Rc1 Qxb4 51. Qc3 $16) 48. Rf2 Qh4 49. Ke2 Qg3 50. Rcf1 Rc7 51. Kd3 Rc4 $2 ({Black returns the favour. With} 51... Rxf2 52. Qxf2 Qh3 $14 {he could keep White's advantage to the minimum}) 52. Qb6 $1 {Now it's all over.} Rd4+ 53. Ke2 Qf4 54. Qxd6+ Kg7 55. Qd7+ Kg8 56. Qc8+ Kg7 57. Qxb7+ Kg8 58. Qc8+ Kg7 59. Qc7+ Kg8 60. Qc8+ Kg7 61. Qc3 $1 Rc4 62. Qd2 Rxe4+ 63. fxe4 Qxe4+ 64. Qe3 Qc2+ 65. Kf3 e4+ 66. Kg3 Qc7+ 67. Rf4 Rc2 68. Qd4+ Kg8 69. Qxe4 gxf4+ 70. Rxf4 1-0


