1. d4 {Efstratios Grivas} e6 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. c4 d5 4. Nc3 Nbd7 5. Bg5 Bb4 6. cxd5 exd5 7. Rc1 c6 8. a3 Be7 ({Of course Black can deviate: a)} 8... Bxc3+ 9. Rxc3 (9. bxc3 Qa5 10. Qb3 Ne4 11. Bh4 O-O $11 {Ribli,Z-Tischbierek,R/Germany 1991}) 9... Qb6 (9... O-O 10. e3 Qe8 11. Bf4 Ne4 12. Rc2 Ndf6 13. Ne5 Qe7 14. Bd3 $14 {Bocharov,D-Vitiugov,N/Plovdiv 2008}) 10. Rb3 (10. Re3+ Ne4 11. Nd2 O-O 12. Nxe4 dxe4 13. Qd2 f5 14. Rg3 Nf6 $13) 10... Qc7 11. e3 (11. Nd2 Ne4 12. Nxe4 dxe4 13. Qc2 Qa5+ 14. Bd2 Qd5 15. Rg3 g6 16. h4 $14 {Gyimesi,Z-Sargissian,G/Germany 2007}) 11... Ne4 12. Bf4 Qa5+ 13. Rb4 O-O 14. Bd3 c5 15. dxc5 Ndxc5 16. O-O $14 {.}) ({b)} 8... Bd6 9. e3 {and now: b2)} O-O ({b1)} 9... Nf8 10. Bd3 (10. Bh4 $6 Ng6 11. Bg3 Bf5 12. b4 a5 13. Qb3 axb4 14. axb4 Be7 $1 $15 {Akesson,R-Aleksandrov,A/Warsaw 2005}) 10... Ng6 11. Qc2 (11. Nh4 $5 O-O 12. Nxg6 fxg6 13. O-O Qe8 14. Bxf6 gxf6 15. e4 dxe4 16. Nxe4 Bf4 17. Rc2 $14 {Grivas,E-Milov,V/Panormo 2002}) 11... O-O 12. h4 $5 (12. O-O h6 13. Bxf6 Qxf6 14. e4 dxe4 15. Nxe4 Qd8 16. Nxd6 Qxd6 17. Bxg6 Qxg6 18. Qxg6 fxg6 19. Rfe1 Bf5 $11 {Petronic,J-Siklosi,Z/Kecskemet 1991}) (12. Bf5 Bxf5 13. Qxf5 Qd7 14. Qxd7 Nxd7 $11 {Sakaev,K-Milov,V/Panormo 2002}) 12... Re8 13. h5 Nf8 14. h6 g6 15. Kf1 $14 {.}) 10. Bd3 Re8 11. O-O (11. Qc2 Nf8 12. O-O Bg4 13. Nd2 Ng6 14. h3 $14 {Hertneck,G-Milov,V/Zillertal 1993}) 11... Nf8 (11... h6 12. Bh4 Nf8 13. Qb3 Ng6 14. Bg3 Bxg3 15. hxg3 Qe7 16. Bxg6 fxg6 17. Ne5 $14 {Bu Xiangzhi-Alekseev,E/Ningpo 2008}) 12. Bh4 (12. Re1 Bg4 (12... h6 13. Bh4 Ng6 14. Bg3 Bxg3 15. hxg3 $14 {Cvitan,O-Landenbergue,C/Wohlen 1993}) 13. Bh4 Ng6 14. Bg3 Ne4 15. Bxd6 Nxd6 16. h3 Bxf3 17. Qxf3 $11 {Evdokimov,A-Aleksandrov,A/Moscow 2008}) (12. e4 dxe4 13. Nxe4 Be7 14. Re1 Nxe4 15. Rxe4 Be6 $11) 12... Ng6 13. Bg3 Bxg3 14. hxg3 Qd6 15. Qc2 Ne7 16. b4 $14 {Lerner,K-Sieglen,J/Boeblingen 1997.}) 9. e3 O-O ({Black's other options are: a)} 9... a5 10. Bd3 O-O 11. Qc2 Re8 12. O-O Nf8 13. Ne5 (13. h3 Be6 14. Rfe1 Nh5 15. Bxe7 Qxe7 16. Na4 g6 17. Nc5 $14 {Teske,H-Horvath,P/Linz 1999}) 13... Ng4 14. Bxe7 Qxe7 15. Nxg4 Bxg4 16. Rce1 Rad8 17. f4 $14 {Grivas,E-Toth,C/Dortmund 1992 (see analysed game).}) ({b)} 9... Ne4 10. Bxe7 (10. Nxe4 dxe4 11. Bxe7 Qxe7 12. Nd2 Nf6 13. Qc2 O-O 14. Qc5 Qe6 15. Be2 Rd8 $11 {Turova,I-Molchanova,T/Chelyabinsk 2008}) (10. Bf4 $6 g5 11. Be5 f6 12. Bg3 h5 13. h4 Nxg3 14. fxg3 g4 15. Ng1 Bd6 16. Kf2 Nb6 $15 {Novikov,I-Krivoshey,S/Alushta 1999}) 10... Qxe7 11. Bd3 Ndf6 (11... O-O 12. O-O f5 13. b4 a6 14. Na4 a5 15. Nc5 axb4 16. axb4 Ndxc5 17. bxc5 $14 {Adianto,U-Handoko,E/Jakarta 1993}) 12. Ne5 Nd6 13. Qc2 O-O 14. O-O $14 {Koneru,H-Satyapragyan,S/Kolkata 2008.}) 10. Bd3 Nh5 ({I do not really like the text move, nor} 10... g6 $6 11. O-O Nh5 12. Bxe7 Qxe7 13. b4 a6 14. Qb3 Ng7 15. a4 Ne8 16. b5 axb5 17. axb5 $16 {Grivas,E-Efthimiatos,G/Athens 1991.}) ({Black should try the natural} 10... Re8 11. O-O (11. h3 Ne4 12. Bxe4 dxe4 13. Bxe7 Qxe7 14. Nd2 f5 15. Qb3+ Kh8 16. Nc4 Nf6 17. Qb4 Be6 $11 {Piket,J-Rainfray,A/France 2001}) (11. Qc2 Nf8 12. O-O Be6 13. h3 N6d7 14. Bf4 Nb6 15. Rfe1 Bd6 16. Bxd6 Qxd6 17. Na4 Nxa4 18. Qxa4 Nd7 19. b4 $14 {Tkachiev,V-Shariyazdanov,A/Kazan 2005}) 11... a5 (11... Ne4 12. Bf4 Nxc3 13. Rxc3 Nf8 14. Qc2 Bg4 15. Ne5 Be6 16. b4 a6 17. Rb1 $14 {Grigorov,G-David,A/Kavala 2008}) 12. Na4 Nf8 13. Ne5 $14 {Smirin,I-Kovacevic,V/Solin 1999.}) 11. Bxe7 Qxe7 12. O-O Ndf6 (12... Nhf6 13. b4 b5 14. a4 a6 15. Qb3 Nb6 16. Rfe1 $14 {.}) 13. b4 $1 g6 14. Qb3 a6 15. a4 {White's minority attack is rolling smoothly.} Ng7 16. b5 axb5 17. axb5 Qa3 $6 (17... Bf5 18. Be2 $14 {.} (18. Bxf5 Nxf5 19. Ne5 c5 $1)) 18. Qxa3 Rxa3 19. bxc6 bxc6 20. Ne5 $16 Bb7 (20... Ba6 21. Bxa6 Rxa6 22. Ne2 Rc8 23. Rc2 $16 {.}) 21. Rc2 (21. Nb1 $5 Rb3 22. Nd2 Ra3 (22... Rxd3 23. Nxd3 Ba6 24. Ne5 Bxf1 25. Kxf1 $18) 23. Rc2 $16 {.}) 21... Rfa8 22. Rb1 R8a7 23. Ne2 Ne6 24. Nc1 Nd8 25. Nb3 (25. f3 Ne8 26. Nb3 f6 27. Nd7 Ne6 28. Ndc5 Nxc5 29. Nxc5 Nd6 30. Kf2 $16 {.}) 25... Ne4 26. h4 $6 (26. f3 {.}) 26... Nd6 27. Nc5 $6 (27. Nd7 Bc8 28. Ndc5 Bf5 29. Bxf5 Nxf5 30. g3 $14 {.}) 27... f6 28. Nf3 Kf7 29. h5 Bc8 30. Rb8 (30. g3 Ra1 31. Rbc1 Bf5 32. hxg6+ hxg6 33. Bxf5 Nxf5 34. Rxa1 Rxa1+ 35. Kg2 Nd6 $11 {.}) 30... Ra8 31. Rcb2 Bf5 32. hxg6+ hxg6 33. Bxf5 Nxf5 34. g4 Nd6 $11 35. g5 Nc4 36. R2b3 Ra1+ 37. Kg2 fxg5 38. Nxg5+ Kf6 39. Nf3 Kf5 40. Rb1 R1a2 41. Kg3 g5 42. Rxa8 Rxa8 43. Rc1 Nf7 44. Rh1 Ncd6 45. Rb1 Nb5 46. Rc1 Ra3 47. Kg2 1/2-1/2


