1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. Bg5 Be7 5. e3 c6 6. Nf3 Nbd7 7. Bd3 O-O ({Passive but playable} 7... b6 8. O-O O-O 9. Qe2 Bb7 10. Rfd1 Re8 11. Rac1 $14 {Grivas,E-Gratseas,S/Iraklion 1997}) ({But Black can also think of inserting} 7... h6 8. Bh4 {and only then} O-O 9. O-O dxc4 (9... Nh5 $6 10. Bxe7 Qxe7 11. Ne5 (11. cxd5 exd5 12. Rb1 a5 13. a3 Nhf6 14. Qc2 Re8 15. b4 axb4 16. axb4 $14 {Grivas,E-Kofidis,A/Karditsa 1995}) 11... Nhf6 12. f4 Nxe5 (12... dxc4 13. Bxc4 Nxe5 (13... c5 14. Qf3 Nb6 15. Bb3 Rd8 16. Rad1 $16 {Gruenwald,M-Barbarics,T/Hungary 2003}) 14. fxe5 $16 {Moldovan,D-Roman,I/Deva 1999}) 13. fxe5 Nd7 14. cxd5 cxd5 (14... exd5 15. Qh5 $16) 15. Rf3 f6 16. exf6 Rxf6 17. Qe2 $16 {Herfel,M-Hummels,O/Giessen 1994}) 10. Bxc4 Nd5 (10... b5 11. Bd3 a6 (11... Bb7 12. Qe2 (12. a3 a5 13. Rc1 b4 14. axb4 axb4 15. Bxf6 Bxf6 16. Ne4 Be7 17. Qb3 Ra5 18. Rfd1 $14 {Bacrot,E-Kekki,P/Izmir 2004}) 12... Rc8 13. Rfd1 a6 14. a4 b4 15. Bxf6 Nxf6 16. Ne4 Nxe4 17. Bxe4 a5 18. Ne5 $16 {Atalik,S-Nikolov,S/Nova Gorica 1999}) 12. a4 b4 13. Bxf6 Nxf6 (13... Bxf6 14. Ne4 Be7 15. Rc1 Bb7 16. Qe2 $14 {Beliavsky,A-Sveshnikov,E/Bled 1999}) 14. Ne4 Bb7 15. Rc1 Rc8 16. Qe2 a5 17. Rfd1 $14 {Ivanchuk,V-Klein,M/Mainz 2007}) 11. Bg3 (11. Bxe7 Qxe7 12. Rc1 Nxc3 13. Rxc3 e5 14. dxe5 Nxe5 15. Nxe5 Qxe5 {½-½ Popov,L-Simic,R/Novi Sad 1981}) 11... Nxc3 (11... N7f6 $5 12. Ne5 Nxc3 (12... Nd7 13. Qc2 Nxe5 14. Bxe5 $14) 13. bxc3 Ne4 14. Qc2 Nxg3 15. hxg3 Bf6 16. Rfd1 (16. Nf3 $6 Qc7 17. Rab1 Rb8 18. Rb2 Re8 $13 {ManVanMelle-Bramson,M/Dos Hermanas 2003}) 16... Qc7 17. Qe4 $14) 12. bxc3 b6 13. e4 (13. Qe2 Bb7 14. Rfd1 b5 15. Bb3 Qa5 16. c4 bxc4 17. Bxc4 c5 18. Rab1 $14 {Grivas,E-Kofidis,A/Iraklion 1995}) 13... Bb7 14. Re1 (14. Qd3 b5 15. Bb3 c5 16. Bc2 c4 17. Qe2 $14 {Agdestein,S-Adianto,U/Novi Sad 1990}) (14. Qe2 Qc8 15. Rad1 Re8 16. Rfe1 $14 {Halkias,S-Bischoff,K/Fuerth 2002}) 14... Nf6 15. Qc2 Re8 16. Rad1 Qc8 17. a4 Nd7 18. Ba2 $14 b5 $6 19. Bb1 a6 20. d5 Nf8 21. d6 Bd8 22. Ne5 Nd7 23. Nxf7 Kxf7 24. e5 Nf8 25. d7 Nxd7 26. Qg6+ Kf8 27. Qh7 Bb6 28. Bg6 {1-0 Halkias,S-Mchedlishvili,M/Yerevan 1999.}) 8. O-O dxc4 9. Bxc4 Nd5 ({The main alternative is} 9... b5 10. Bd3 Bb7 (10... a6 11. e4 Bb7 12. e5 Nd5 13. Bxe7 Qxe7 14. Nxd5 cxd5 15. Re1 (15. Qd2 $5 Rac8 (15... f5 16. Rac1 Rac8 17. Qa5 Nb8 18. Qb6 $14 {Kantorik,M-Salac,J/Prague 1992}) (15... Rfc8 16. h4 Nf8 17. h5 h6 18. g3 Rc7 19. Kg2 Rac8 20. Rh1 $14 {Sisask,J-Safaryan,A/Dos Hermanas 2004}) 16. Rac1 (16. Ng5 g6 17. Nh3 f6 $13 {Guichard,P-Tatard,M/Hyeres 2002}) 16... Nb6 17. b3 $14) 15... Rac8 16. Qe2 Nb6 17. h4 $14 {Graf,A-Bakatselos,H/Thessaloniki 2007}) 11. Rc1 (11. a3 a6 $1 (11... a5 12. Qc2 h6 13. Bxf6 Nxf6 14. Ne5 $14 {Grivas,E-Agistriotis,M/Corfu 1996}) 12. b4 a5 13. Qb3 c5 $1 14. Nxb5 cxb4 15. axb4 axb4 $13 {Morales Mendoza,L-Zapata,K/Lima 2004}) 11... a6 12. Qc2 Rc8 13. Rfd1 (13. Bxf6 Nxf6 14. Ne4 Nxe4 15. Bxe4 f5 $1 16. Bd3 c5 $13 {Bacrot,E-Rainfray,A/France 1997}) (13. Ne5 c5 $1 14. Nxd7 Qxd7 15. dxc5 Rxc5 16. Bxf6 Bxf6 17. Bxh7+ Kh8 18. Be4 Bxe4 19. Qxe4 Qc7 $11) 13... h6 14. Bxf6 Nxf6 15. Ne5 $14 {(15...} c5 16. dxc5 Qc7 17. c6 Bxc6 18. Nxc6 Qxc6 19. Nd5 Qxd5 20. Qxc8 Rxc8 21. Rxc8+ Bf8 22. Bh7+ Nxh7 23. Rxd5 exd5 24. Ra8 $14 {).}) 10. Bxe7 Qxe7 11. e4 $5 ({This is the most critical line. The alternative is} 11. Qc2 Nxc3 12. Qxc3 (12. bxc3 b6 (12... e5 13. Qe4 $1 Re8 14. a4 a5 15. Rab1 Rb8 16. Rb3 (16. Bd3 g6 17. Nxe5 Nxe5 18. Qxe5 Qxe5 19. dxe5 Rxe5 20. Rb6 Rc5 21. Rc1 $14) 16... Nf6 $2 (16... exd4 17. Qxe7 Rxe7 18. cxd4 $16) 17. Qxe5 Qxe5 18. Nxe5 $18 {Ullrich,M-Allietta,E/Bellheim 1994}) 13. a4 Bb7 14. Bd3 h6 15. a5 c5 16. Be4 Bxe4 17. Qxe4 Nf6 18. Qd3 Rac8 19. Rfb1 $14 {Chatalbashev,B-Jedynak,R/Thessaloniki 2007}) 12... b6 13. Qd3 Bb7 14. Ba6 Rab8 15. Bxb7 Rxb7 16. Rac1 Rc7 17. Rc2 $14 {Zhang Pengxiang-Roos,L/Kemer 2007.}) (11. Ne4 {is analysed in the game Wells,P-Gurevich,M/Gibraltar 2006.}) 11... Nxc3 12. bxc3 b6 ({The other option is} 12... e5 13. Re1 (13. Qd2 exd4 14. cxd4 Nb6 15. Bd3 Be6 16. Rfe1 Rad8 17. Qf4 Rfe8 18. a4 $14 {Christiansen,L-Kogan,B/Reykjavik 1986}) (13. Qc2 b5 14. Bd3 Bb7 15. Rae1 a6 16. Nxe5 Nxe5 17. dxe5 Qxe5 18. f4 Qc5+ 19. Kh1 Rae8 20. e5 $14 {Vaysman,A-Opravil,K/Pardubice 1992}) 13... Rd8 (13... exd4 14. cxd4 Nb6 15. Bb3 Bg4 16. h3 (16. Qd3 Bxf3 17. Qxf3 Rad8 18. Rad1 Rfe8 19. a4 $14 {Lasker,Em-Mason,J/London 1899}) 16... Bxf3 17. Qxf3 Rad8 18. Qc3 (18. Rad1 Rd7 $6 (18... Qb4 19. a3 Qa5 $14) 19. Qc3 $1 $16 {Kortschnoj,V-Casagrande,H/Linz 1997}) 18... Rd6 19. a4 Rfd8 20. Rad1 $14 {Kortschnoj,V-Kolarov,A/Bucharest 1966}) (13... c5 14. Qd2 cxd4 15. cxd4 exd4 16. Nxd4 Ne5 17. Bb3 Rd8 18. Qc3 Bg4 19. Bd5 $14 {Gligoric,S-Lim Kok Ann/Manila 1968}) 14. Qb3 exd4 15. cxd4 Nb6 16. Bf1 Bg4 17. Ne5 (17. Rad1 Rd7 18. h3 Bxf3 19. Qxf3 Rad8 20. d5 cxd5 21. Bb5 Rd6 22. exd5 Qf8 $11) 17... Be6 (17... Bh5 $5 18. Qh3 (18. Qe3 f6 19. Nc4 Nxc4 20. Bxc4+ Bf7 21. Rac1 $11) 18... Rxd4 19. Qxh5 g6 20. Nxc6 bxc6 21. Qf3 Qe5 22. Qe3 $14) 18. Qc3 $1 (18. Qe3 f6 19. Nf3 Qb4 20. a4 Nc4 $13 {Kortschnoj,V-Schweber,S/Stockholm 1962}) 18... Rd6 19. h3 Rad8 20. Nf3 $14 {.}) 13. Re1 Bb7 14. a4 ({White seems to have an enjoyable position as he can also choose between: a)} 14. Bd3 Rfd8 15. Re3 Nf8 16. c4 c5 17. d5 $14 {Kortschnoj,V-Segal,A/Sao Paulo 1979.}) ({b)} 14. Qd2 Rfd8 15. Rad1 h6 16. Qf4 Rac8 17. h4 $14 {Kurz,A-Glienke,M/Germany 1988.}) ({c)} 14. Bb3 Rad8 $14 {Kjolberg,J-Knutsen,H/Oslo 2007.}) 14... Rfd8 (14... Rad8 15. Qb3 Nf6 16. a5 (16. Rad1 c5 17. d5 exd5 18. exd5 Qd6 19. Be2 Rfe8 20. c4 $14 {Fransson,O-Braby,B/Rodeby 1998}) 16... c5 17. Bd3 $14 {.}) 15. Qb3 Rac8 16. a5 $1 $14 b5 17. a6 Ba8 18. Bf1 Rb8 19. Qa2 $6 (19. Rab1 e5 20. h3 $14 {.}) 19... Rb6 20. c4 Nb8 $6 (20... c5 $2 21. cxb5 cxd4 22. Nxd4 Nc5 23. Qa3 Rxd4 24. Rac1 $16) (20... e5 $1 21. cxb5 exd4 22. Nxd4 cxb5 23. Nxb5 Nc5 $11 {.}) 21. Qd2 c5 $6 (21... e5 22. cxb5 exd4 23. Nxd4 cxb5 24. Rad1 $14 {.}) 22. cxb5 cxd4 23. Rad1 $2 (23. Nxd4 $1 Rbd6 24. Qb4 $16 {.}) 23... e5 $13 24. Rb1 Nd7 25. Qb4 Kf8 26. Nd2 Rd6 27. Bd3 Nb6 28. Rec1 R6d7 29. Qxe7+ Kxe7 30. Nc4 Nxc4 31. Rxc4 f5 32. f3 fxe4 33. fxe4 Rf8 $6 (33... Rb8 $1 $13 {.}) 34. b6 $1 axb6 35. Rxb6 Rf4 $2 (35... Rf6 $1 36. Rxf6 Kxf6 37. Rc8 Ra7 38. Kf2 $14 {.}) 36. Rc5 $1 $18 Rf6 37. Rxe5+ Kf7 38. Rb8 Ra7 39. h3 Rd6 40. Ree8 Bc6 41. Rf8+ Ke7 42. Rg8 Kf6 43. Rbf8+ Ke5 44. Rf5+ Ke6 45. Bc4+ 1-0


