1. d4 {Ribli Zoltan} Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. g3 d5 4. Bg2 Be7 5. O-O O-O 6. c4 dxc4 7. Qc2 a6 8. a4 Bd7 9. Qxc4 Bc6 10. Bf4 a5 11. Nc3 Na6 12. Rfe1 Nb4 13. Rac1 Nfd5 14. Nxd5 exd5 15. Qb3 b6 $6 (15... Bd6 {½-½ Lopez,C - Alvarez,J Capablanca Premier-B, 1977(15)} 16. Ne5 $14) 16. Ne5 Bb7 (16... Be8 17. e4 c6 18. exd5 cxd5 19. Bd2 $16) 17. Nd3 $6 (17. Nd7 $1 Qxd7 18. Rxc7 $16) 17... Nxd3 18. Qxd3 Bd6 19. Bxd6 Qxd6 20. Rc2 f5 21. Rec1 Rf7 22. Qb5 Rd8 23. b4 $5 axb4 24. a5 Ra8 25. axb6 c6 26. Qc5 Qxc5 27. dxc5 Rff8 28. Bxd5+ $5 cxd5 29. c6 Rab8 30. cxb7 Rxb7 31. Rc6 Rfb8 32. Rc8+ Kf7 (32... Rxc8 $2 33. Rxc8+ Kf7 34. Rc7+ $18) 33. R8c7+ Ke6 34. R7c6+ Ke5 35. f4+ Ke4 36. Re6+ Kd4 37. Kf2 Rxb6 38. Re3 g5 39. Rd3+ {Black's king is in a mating net.  Der schwarze König befindet sich in Mattnetz.} Ke4 40. Re3+ (40. Rcd1 $1 gxf4 41. Rxd5 fxg3+ 42. hxg3 $18) 40... Kd4 41. Kf3 g4+ 42. Kf2 Rh6 43. h4 1-0


