1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6 3. g3 Bg7 4. Bg2 O-O 5. O-O d6 6. a4 a5 7. Nc3 d5 $5 8. Ne5 ({As usual, White has some other interesting alternatives at his disposal: a)} 8. Bf4 c6 9. Qd2 Bf5 10. Nh4 Be6 11. Bh6 Qb6 12. Bxg7 Kxg7 13. f4 c5 14. e3 Nc6 15. Nb5 Rad8 16. f5 Bc8 17. c3 $36 {Rashkovsky,N-Loginov,V/Balassagyarmat 1990}) ({b)} 8. Re1 {b3)} Nc6 $1 ({b1)} 8... Bf5 9. Nh4 Be6 10. e4 dxe4 11. Nxe4 Nxe4 12. Bxe4 c6 13. c3 Nd7 (13... Na6 14. Ng2 Nc7 15. Nf4 Bd5 16. Nxd5 Nxd5 17. Bxd5 cxd5 18. Qe2 e6 19. Qb5 $14 {Romanishin,O-Tratar,M/Nova Gorica 1999}) 14. Bg2 Bd5 15. Bxd5 cxd5 16. Qb3 Nb6 17. Nf3 Re8 18. Bf4 $14 {Romanishin,O-Golubev,M/Donetsk 1998}) ({b2)} 8... Ne4 9. Nxe4 dxe4 10. Ng5 (10. Ne5 c5 11. c3 cxd4 12. cxd4 Qd5 $13 {Wells,P-Arbakov,V/Passau 1995}) 10... Qxd4 11. Qxd4 Bxd4 12. c3 Bb6 13. Nxe4 Na6 14. Nd2 c6 15. Nc4 Bc7 $14 {½-½ Supancic,D-Tratar,M/Bled 1999}) 9. Ne5 Nb4 10. Nb5 c6 11. Na3 Qb6 12. c3 Na6 13. Nd3 Bf5 14. Bf4 Rfe8 15. Be5 Bf8 16. Bf4 Bg7 17. Bg5 Bf8 18. Bf4 {½-½ Romanishin,O-Baklan,V/Istanbul 2003}) ({c)} 8. Be3 c6 9. Qd2 Qb6 10. Ne5 Ng4 11. Nxg4 Bxg4 12. h3 Bf5 $11 {Djurkovic,M-Cvitan,O/Nova Gorica 1996}) 8... Bf5 ({For} 8... c6 {see Grivas,E-Vouldis,A/Athens 1996}) 9. Nxd5 $6 ({This offers nothing to White.} 9. g4 $5 Nxg4 (9... Be6 10. g5 Nfd7 11. Nxd5 Nxe5 12. dxe5 Bxe5 13. Nf4 Bc8 14. Nd3 Bg7 15. Bf4 $14) 10. Nxg4 Bxg4 11. Nxd5 c6 12. Ne3 Be6 13. d5 cxd5 14. Nxd5 Nc6 15. c3 $14 {deserves attention.}) 9... Nxd5 10. e4 Be6 11. exd5 Bxd5 12. Bxd5 (12. Re1 Bxg2 13. Kxg2 Nd7 14. Nxd7 Qxd7 15. c3 $11) 12... Qxd5 13. Qf3 Rd8 (13... Qxd4 14. Qxb7 Ra7 15. c3 Rxb7 16. cxd4 Rd8 17. Be3 Rxb2 18. Rfc1 c6 19. Nxc6 Nxc6 20. Rxc6 Bxd4 21. Bxd4 Rxd4 22. Rc5 $11) 14. Re1 Bxe5 15. Qxd5 Rxd5 16. Rxe5 Rxe5 17. dxe5 Nc6 18. Bf4 Nd4 (18... Rd8 19. c3 e6 20. h4 $11) 19. c3 (19. Rd1 Ne2+ 20. Kg2 Nxf4+ 21. gxf4 $11) 19... Ne2+ 20. Kf1 Nxf4 21. gxf4 Rd8 22. Ke2 $11 Kf8 23. Ra3 Ke8 24. Rb3 b6 25. Rb5 e6 26. Rb3 Rd5 27. Ra3 Kd7 28. Ra1 Kc6 29. h4 h5 30. Ke3 Kd7 31. Rg1 Ke7 