1. Nf3 {Efstratios Grivas Efstratios Grivas Efstratios Grivas: 'Grivas,Efstratios Grivas,Efstratios: 'Efstratios Grivas''} Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. d4 d5 4. Nc3 Bb4 5. cxd5 exd5 6. Bg5 Nbd7 7. Rc1 c6 8. a3 Be7 9. e3 a5 10. Bd3 O-O 11. Qc2 Re8 12. O-O Nf8 13. Ne5 Ng4 14. Bxe7 Qxe7 15. Nxg4 Bxg4 16. Rce1 Rad8 17. f4 $14 {White can create a kingside initiative. On the other hand Black is quite slow on the other side of the board.} Bh5 18. Qf2 f6 (18... Nd7 19. f5 Nf6 20. h3 $16 {.}) 19. Qh4 Bg6 $6 (19... Bf7 20. Rf3 $14 {.}) 20. f5 Bf7 21. Rf3 Kh8 (21... Nd7 22. Rg3 Qd6 23. Ne2 Re7 24. Qg4 Be8 25. Nf4 $16 {.}) 22. Ref1 Qd6 23. Rg3 Re7 24. Ne2 b6 25. Rf4 $1 (25. Nf4 c5 26. a4 cxd4 27. exd4 $14 {.}) 25... c5 26. Rfg4 c4 $2 (26... Be8 27. Nf4 c4 28. Bc2 $16 {.}) 27. Bc2 $2 (27. Rxg7 cxd3 28. Qh6 $18 {.}) 27... Be8 28. Nf4 {Efstratios Grivas: '' '' Efstratios Grivas: ''Grivas,Efstratios: '' 'Efstratios Grivas: '' Efstratios Grivas: '.''' .'} c3 $6 (28... Kg8 29. Qh6 Rdd7 30. Ne6 $16 {.}) 29. bxc3 $6 ({In a tactical position both players failed to act properly. White could win once more with} 29. Ne6 $1 Nxe6 30. fxe6 g5 31. Qh6 $18 {.}) 29... Qxa3 30. h3 $1 {An excellent tactical idea and probably the only move to keep White's advantage alive.} Qd6 $6 (30... Qc1+ 31. Kh2 Qxc2 32. Qxf6 $1 $18) (30... Qxc3 31. Kh2 $1 Qc6 32. Qh6 Rdd7 33. Bb3 $16 {.}) 31. Ne6 $1 Nxe6 32. fxe6 g5 (32... g6 33. Bxg6 Bxg6 34. Rxg6 Qxe6 35. Rxf6 Qd7 36. Qf4 $18 {.}) 33. Qh6 $18 Bg6 (33... Rg7 34. Bxh7 Rxh7 35. Qxf6+ Rg7 36. Rxg5 {.}) 34. Bxg6 Qxe6 35. Bc2 b5 36. Rf3 Rf7 37. Rxg5 Qe7 38. Rgf5 Rd6 39. Bb3 1-0


