1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 Nf6 4. Nc3 Be7 5. Bg5 O-O 6. e3 h6 7. Bh4 b6 8. Bd3 Bb7 (8... Ba6 9. Bxf6 Bxf6 10. cxd5 Bxd3 11. Qxd3 exd5 12. O-O c6 13. b4 $14 {Grivas,E-Kinopoulos,A/Athens 2006.}) 9. O-O Nbd7 ({Alternatives as} 9... c5 10. Qe2 Ne4 11. Bxe7 Qxe7 12. cxd5 (12. Rac1 Nd7 13. cxd5 exd5 14. dxc5 (14. Ba6 Ndf6 15. Bxb7 Qxb7 16. dxc5 bxc5 17. Nxe4 Nxe4 18. Rc2 Rac8 19. Rfc1 Rfd8 20. h3 a5 21. Nd2 {½-½ Grivas,E-Boensch,U/Athens 1997}) 14... Nxc3 15. Rxc3 bxc5 16. Ba6 Bxa6 17. Qxa6 Nf6 18. Rfc1 Ne4 19. R3c2 Rfd8 20. Qd3 Rd7 21. Nd2 Nxd2 22. Qxd2 c4 23. Rd1 Rad8 24. Qd4 f6 25. Kf1 $14 Qe5 $6 26. Qxe5 fxe5 27. e4 dxe4 28. Rxd7 Rxd7 29. Rxc4 Rd2 30. Rxe4 Rxb2 31. Ra4 Rb7 32. Ra5 $16 {Grivas,E-Daniilidis,A/Athens 1984}) 12... exd5 13. Rfd1 {or}) (9... Ne4 10. Bxe7 Qxe7 11. Qe2 {transposes.}) 10. Qe2 (10. cxd5 Nxd5 11. Nxd5 Bxd5 12. Bxe7 Qxe7 13. Qe2 {(½-½ Kramnik,V-Spassky,B/Zuerich 2001)} Rad8 14. Bc4 Bb7 15. Rfd1 e5 $11 {Grivas,E-Graf,A/Porto Carras 1998.}) 10... c5 (10... dxc4 {transposes to the analysed game Grivas,E-Gabriel,Ch/Budapest 1994.}) 11. Rfd1 Ne4 ({The main alternative is} 11... cxd4 12. Nxd4 {and now:} {c)} Rc8 ({a)} 12... Ne5 13. Bxf6 Bxf6 14. cxd5 Nxd3 15. Qxd3 Bxd5 (15... exd5 16. Rd2 Rc8 17. Rad1 Re8 18. Nde2 Be5 19. Qb5 Qf6 20. Qa4 Bb8 21. Qd7 Bc6 22. Qg4 $14 {Trifunovic,P-Pilnik,H/Mar del Plata 1953}) 16. Qe2 Rc8 (16... Qd7 17. Ndb5 a6 18. Nxd5 Qxb5 19. Nxf6+ gxf6 20. Qg4+ Kh7 21. Qd4 Kg7 22. a4 $14 {Schmidt,W-Abramovic,B/Vrnjacka Banja 1983}) (16... Bb7 $2 17. Nxe6 fxe6 18. Rxd8 Rfxd8 19. Rd1 Rxd1+ 20. Qxd1 Rd8 21. Qe2 Bxc3 22. bxc3 Be4 23. h4 Bd3 24. Qg4 Kf7 25. Qa4 {1-0 Schmidt,W-Staniszewski,P/Poznan 1997}) 17. Ndb5 Rc5 18. Ne4 (18. Nxd5 exd5 19. Rd2 Qd7 20. Nd4 Rfc8 21. Rad1 Qa4 22. b3 Qa5 23. g3 Rc1 24. Kg2 Rxd1 25. Rxd1 Rc5 26. h4 $14 {Gheorghiu,F-Petrosian,A/Bagneux 1982}) 18... Rc4 19. Nbc3 Be5 20. f4 Bxc3 21. Nxc3 Qc7 22. Nxd5 exd5 23. Rxd5 Rc2 24. Rd2 $14 {Bacrot,E-Naiditsch,A/Corsica 2005.}) ({b)} 12... Nc5 13. Bc2 $1 (13. cxd5 Nxd5 14. Bxe7 Nxc3 15. Bxd8 Nxe2+ 16. Bxe2 Rfxd8 $11 {Lendero,P-Zagozen,D/Novo Mesto 2000}) 13... Nfe4 14. Nxe4 Bxh4 15. Nc3 Ba6 16. Ndb5 Bxb5 17. Nxb5 Qd7 18. cxd5 exd5 19. Nc3 $16 {Liu Yang-Pham T Thu,H/Vung Tau 2004.}) 13. Bg3 $1 (13. Rac1 Ne5 14. cxd5 (14. Bxf6 Bxf6 15. cxd5 Nxd3 16. Qxd3 Bxd5 17. Qb1 (17. Nxd5 Qxd5 18. b3 Bxd4 19. exd4 Rfd8 20. Rxc8 Rxc8 $15 {Sismanis,A-Bolsakovs,V/Litohoro 1999}) (17. Qe2 Bxd4 $1 18. Rxd4 Qg5) 17... Qd7 18. Nxd5 exd5 19. g3 Rxc1 20. Qxc1 Rc8 21. Qd2 Bxd4 22. Qxd4 Qb5 23. a4 Qc4 24. Qxc4 dxc4 25. Rd7 {½-½ Ftacnik,L-Cvetkovic,S/Stary Smokovec 1983}) 14... Nxd3 (14... Nxd5 15. Bxe7 (15. Nxd5 $2 Qxd5 $19 {Michielsen,J-Havinga,J/Nijmegen 2001}) 15... Qxe7 16. Nxd5 Bxd5 17. Ba6 Rxc1 18. Rxc1 $11) 15. Qxd3 Nxd5 16. Bxe7 Qxe7 17. Nxd5 Bxd5 $11 {Zweschper,E-Hoeck,R/Wiesbaden 1988}) 13... Nc5 14. Bc2 a6 {(½-½ Giorgadze,T-Lobron,E/Dortmund 1984)} (14... Bd6 15. e4 (15. Bxd6 Qxd6 16. Ndb5 Qb8 17. cxd5 Nxd5 (17... a6 18. Nd4 Nxd5 19. Nxd5 Bxd5 20. e4 Bb7 21. b4 $16) 18. Nxd5 Bxd5 19. e4 Bc6 20. Nd6 Rcd8 21. e5 $14) 15... Bxg3 16. hxg3 Re8 $6 (16... e5 17. Nf5 $14) 17. e5 Nh7 18. cxd5 $16 {Grivas,E-Papathanasiou,A/Kallithea 2003}) 15. Rac1 Bd6 16. cxd5 (16. Bxd6 Qxd6 17. cxd5 Nxd5 18. Nxd5 Qxd5 19. f3 Qg5 20. b4 $14) 16... Bxg3 17. hxg3 Nxd5 18. Nxd5 Qxd5 19. f3 Qe5 20. b4 $1 $14 {.}) 12. Bxe7 Qxe7 13. cxd5 Nxc3 $6 ({Black should also take into account the alternative} 13... exd5 14. Ba6 (14. Rac1 Nxc3 $1 (14... Ndf6 15. dxc5 bxc5 16. Bxe4 dxe4 17. Nd2 $14 {Graf,A-Schlosberg,E/Regensburg 1998}) 15. bxc3 c4 16. Bb1 b5 $11 {Aseev,K-Rustemov,A/Ekaterinburg 2002}) (14. dxc5 Nxc3 (14... Ndxc5 15. Rac1 $14) 15. bxc3 Nxc5 (15... bxc5 16. c4) 16. Nd4 Rac8 17. a4 Ne4 18. Bxe4 dxe4 19. a5 Rxc3 20. axb6 axb6 21. Qb2 Qc5 {½-½ Aleshin,O-Rjabzev,K/Essentuki 2003}) 14... Nxc3 (14... Bxa6 15. Qxa6 Ndf6 {Petrosian,T-Geller,E/Leningrad 1977}) (14... Ndf6 15. Bxb7 Qxb7 16. dxc5 bxc5 17. Rac1 Rab8 18. b3 Nxc3 19. Rxc3 Qb4 20. Rc2 Rfc8 21. Rdc1 a5 22. Ne1 Qb6 23. Nd3 $14 {Panno,O-Rubinetti,J/Rio Hondo 1987}) 15. bxc3 Nf6 16. Bxb7 Qxb7 17. dxc5 (17. a4 Ne4 18. Qb2 Rfc8 19. Nd2 Nd6 20. Rdb1 cxd4 21. cxd4 Rc6 $13) 17... bxc5 18. Rab1 Qc6 19. Qb5 (19. c4 $5) 19... Qxb5 20. Rxb5 Ne4 21. Rb3 Rfd8 22. Ne5 Rab8 23. Ra3 $14 {.}) 14. bxc3 exd5 (14... Bxd5 15. a4 (15. c4 Bb7 16. Rac1 Qf6 17. Bb1 Bxf3 18. Qxf3 Qxf3 19. gxf3 Rfd8 $11 {Khaled,R-Mokgacha,K/Abuja 2003}) 15... cxd4 16. cxd4 Rfc8 (16... e5 17. e4 $1 (17. Nxe5 $6 Nxe5 18. dxe5 Qxe5 19. Bb5 Rfd8 20. Rd4 Bb3 21. Qf3 Bd5 22. Qe2 {½-½ Schmidt,W-Ahlander,B/Naestved 1988}) 17... Be6 18. d5 Bg4 19. a5 $14) 17. a5 $14 {.}) 15. a4 Rac8 16. a5 $14 {White has achieved pressure on the queenside and generally he seems to have a plan in contrast to Black who has to remain passive.} cxd4 $6 (16... Bc6 17. axb6 axb6 18. Bb5 $14 {.}) 17. cxd4 Rc7 18. Qb2 Qe6 19. axb6 axb6 20. h3 $16 Ra8 21. Rxa8+ Bxa8 22. Qa3 $1 Qc6 23. Rb1 g6 $2 (23... Bb7 24. Qe7 Nf8 25. Qd8 $16 {.}) 24. Bb5 $1 Qb7 25. Ra1 Rc8 26. Ba6 1-0


