1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nf3 Bg7 4. g3 O-O 5. Bg2 d6 6. O-O Nc6 7. Nc3 Bf5 8. Bg5 {(D) } h6 9. Bd2 (9. Be3 Qd7 10. d5 Na5 11. b3 c6 12. Rc1 Bh3 {Kurajica,B-Mujic,H/Neum 2000}) (9. Bxf6 Bxf6 10. Qd2 Bg7 $11) 9... e5 $6 ({Preferable is} 9... Qd7 10. d5 Nd8 11. Re1 Bh3 12. Bh1 e5 13. e4 c5 14. dxc6 bxc6 15. c5 Ne6 16. cxd6 Qxd6 $13 {Guliev,S-Kondenko,A/Yalta 1996. Black should keep a flexible centre.}) 10. d5 Ne7 11. Nh4 Bd7 12. e4 g5 13. Nf3 Ng6 14. Ne1 g4 15. Nc2 $14 h5 16. Ne3 Nh7 $6 ({Clearly better is} 16... h4 17. f3 hxg3 18. hxg3 gxf3 19. Qxf3 Ne7 20. g4 $14) 17. Nf5 $1 Bxf5 18. exf5 Ne7 19. f3 $1 $16 Nxf5 20. fxg4 Nd4 $5 21. gxh5 f5 22. Ne2 Ng5 23. Nxd4 exd4 24. Qc2 Qf6 25. g4 Nf7 26. Qxf5 Qxf5 27. Rxf5 Ne5 28. Rxf8+ Rxf8 29. g5 $2 ({Not that difficult is} 29. h6 Bh8 30. b3 Nxg4 31. Rf1 $16) 29... Nxc4 30. Be1 d3 31. Bc3 $2 ({White should concentrate on drawing the game:} 31. Rd1 Nxb2 32. Rc1 d2 33. Bxd2 Bd4+ 34. Kh1 Nd3 35. Rxc7 Nf2+ $11) 31... Bxc3 32. bxc3 d2 $2 ({Returning the favour. Winning was} 32... Ne3 33. Bf1 Rxf1+ 34. Rxf1 d2 $19) 33. Rd1 Rf5 $1 34. h4 Rf4 35. Bf1 $6 ({A better try is} 35. Bh3 Rxh4 36. Be6+ Kh8 37. Bc8 Rxh5 38. Bxb7 Rxg5+ 39. Kf2 $17) 35... Ne3 36. Rxd2 Rxf1+ 37. Kh2 Nf5 38. Kh3 Rf4 39. h6 Rxh4+ 40. Kg2 Rg4+ (40... Kh7 $19) 41. Kf3 Rxg5 (41... Rc4 $19) 42. Kf4 Rh5 $2 ({Black loses his way in the last moves. Still winning is} 42... Nh4 43. Rh2 Rh5 44. Kg4 Rxh6 $19) 43. Kg4 Rxh6 44. Kxf5 Kf7 45. Re2 Rh3 46. Rc2 Rf3+ 47. Ke4 Rf1 48. c4 b6 49. Kd4 Ke7 50. Re2+ Kd7 51. Kc3 Rf3+ 52. Kb4 (52. Kc2 $15) 52... a6 53. a4 Rf4 54. a5 $2 ({The final mistake. White should have played} 54. Rh2 c5+ 55. Kb3 $15) 54... b5 55. Rc2 c6 56. dxc6+ Kxc6 57. Kb3 bxc4+ 58. Rxc4+ Rxc4 59. Kxc4 d5+ 60. Kd4 Kd6 61. Kd3 Kc5 62. Kc3 Kb5 63. Kd4 Kxa5 64. Kxd5 Kb4 65. Kd4 a5 66. Kd3 Kb3 67. Kd2 Kb2 0-1


