4 16. Bd2 $1 Re8 17. Bxa5 Qd7 18. Qg3 $18) 16. Qg3 Bf8 17. Nxh6+ Kh7 18. Nxf7 $18) 15. Nf5 Nh5 $1 (15... Bf8 16. Qg3 $16 Nh5 17. Nxh6+ Kh7 18. Qg4 Nxf4 19. Nxf7 Ne2+ 20. Kh1 $18 {[%cal Gg4h5]}) 16. Qf2 b5 17. Bb3 Nxf4 18. Qxf4 $14) 14... Nxc4 15. dxc4 Re8 {Black goes on a right plan. Better later, than never!} 16. Kh1 {White is waiting for black's f8, thus black will not be able to occupy a long diagonal immediately.} Bf8 17. Qg3 Ne4 {looks very logical.} (17... Nh5 18. Qg4 Nxf4 (18... Nf6 $5 19. Qf5 (19. Qh3 $5) 19... Qc8 20. Qd3) 19. Qxf4 $14 {[%cal Ga1e1]}) 18. Qg4 (18. Qh3 Qc8) 18... Qc8 $1 19. Qh5 $2 (19. Qxc8 Raxc8 20. Rae1 $11) 19... g6 20. Qh4 g5 21. Bxg5 hxg5 22. Nxg5 Nxg5 23. Qxg5+ Bg7 $17 24. Rf5 Qd8 25. Qh5 Qe7 26. Raf1 Rf8 27. h3 Rae8 28. R1f4 Qe1+ 29. Kh2 Re5 30. Rh4 Qxh4 31. Qxh4 Rxf5 32. Qe7 Be5+ 33. Kg1 b5 34. cxb5 axb5 35. c3 Rf4 36. Qg5+ 1/2-1/2


