1. e4 {Efstratios Grivas} c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 d6 4. Bxc6+ bxc6 5. O-O ({Black's plan is to play ...e5 and then concentrate on an eventual ...f5, exploiting his bishop-pair. Therefore, White is more or less obliged to go for a d4-advance or not to allow Black to realise his idea of ...e5. His other options are:  a)} 5. e5 dxe5 $1 6. Nxe5 Qd5 7. Nf3 Bg4 (7... Qe4+ 8. Qe2 Qxc2 9. Nc3 Nf6 10. Ne5 Nd7 11. O-O Nxe5 12. Qxe5 Qf5 13. Qc7 Qd7 14. Qa5 g6 15. d3 Bg7 16. Be3 O-O 17. Bxc5 Qxd3 18. Bxe7 Re8 19. Rad1 Qc2 20. Ba3 Bg4 21. f3 Bf5 $13 {Rausis,I-Dreev,A/Tallinn 2009}) 8. d3 Bxf3 9. Qxf3 Qxf3 10. gxf3 Nf6 11. Be3 e6 12. Nd2 Nd7 13. O-O-O Bd6 14. Nb3 Ke7 $11 {Predojevic,B-Malakhov,V/Sarajevo 2006.}) ({b)} 5. d4 cxd4 6. Qxd4 e5 (6... Qb6 7. c4 Qxd4 8. Nxd4 Bb7 9. Nc3 Nf6 10. f3 g6 11. Be3 Bg7 12. Rc1 Nd7 $11 {Hlavnicka,K-Seifarth,R/Czech Rep. 1997}) 7. Qd1 (7. Qd3 Be7 8. O-O Nf6 9. Bg5 h6 10. Bxf6 gxf6 11. c4 Qd7 12. Nh4 Qg4 13. g3 Rg8 14. Kh1 Rb8 15. b3 d5 $1 $13 {Guennoun,A-Saez,F/Laragne 2002}) 7... Nf6 8. Nc3 Be7 9. O-O Bg4 10. h3 Bh5 11. Re1 O-O 12. Be3 Qc7 $15 {Jung,H-Ali Laith,A/Beijing 2008.}) ({c)} 5. h3 e5 6. O-O Be7 (6... g5 $5 7. b4 (7. d3 g4 8. hxg4 Bxg4 9. Nbd2 Ne7 10. Qe1 Rg8 11. Nh4 Ng6 12. Nxg6 Rxg6 13. f3 Bh3 14. Rf2 Qh4 15. Qe2 Bh6 $13 {Spasov,V-Rogers,I/Groningen 1989}) 7... h5 8. bxc5 g4 9. Nh2 gxh3 10. g3 dxc5 11. Bb2 Bd6 12. Na3 Be6 $13 {Wagner,A-Stripunsky,A/Pardubice 1994}) (6... f5 7. exf5 Bxf5 8. Re1 Be7 9. b4 cxb4 10. a3 b3 11. cxb3 Nf6 12. Nc3 c5 13. d3 Rc8 14. Ne4 O-O $13 {Montheard,X-Belkhodja,S/Evry 2005}) 7. c3 (7. Re1 g5 8. g4 h5 9. Nh2 hxg4 10. hxg4 Nf6 11. f3 Be6 $17 {Maitesian,S-Dgebuadze,A/Nice 2000}) 7... f5 8. d4 fxe4 9. Nfd2 exd4 10. cxd4 d5 11. dxc5 Ba6 $15 {Arapovic,V-Palac,M/Makarska 1996.}) 5... e5 (5... Bg4 {is not that bad:  a)} 6. c3 ({b)} 6. d3 e5 (6... e6 7. Nbd2 Nf6 8. Re1 Nd7 9. h3 Bh5 10. Nf1 Be7 11. Ng3 Bg6 12. b3 O-O 13. Bb2 Re8 $11 {Kritz,L-Wang Yue/Gibraltar 2008}) (6... Nf6 7. Bg5 Nd7 8. Nbd2 f6 9. Bh4 e5 10. Nc4 Be7 11. Ne3 Be6 12. c3 Rb8 13. b3 d5 14. Nd2 g6 $11 {Ivanchuk,V-Topalov,V/Wijk aan Zee 2003}) 7. Nbd2 Nf6 8. Nc4 Nd7 9. Ne3 Be6 10. c3 Be7 11. d4 f6 $11 {Shirov,A-Vallejo Pons,F/Monte Carlo 2005.}) ({c)} 6. h3 Bh5 7. e5 e6 (7... dxe5 8. g4 e4 $1 9. gxh5 exf3 10. Nc3 Rc8 11. Qxf3 e6 $13 {Rublevsky,S-Dreev,A/Moscow 2005}) 8. exd6 Bxd6 9. d3 Ne7 10. Nbd2 O-O 11. Ne4 Nd5 12. Re1 Re8 13. Ng3 Bg6 $13 {Shirov,A-Gelfand,B/Dortmund 2002.}) 6... Nf6 7. h3 (7. d3 Nd7 (7... e5 8. h3 Bh5 9. Bg5 Be7 10. Nbd2 O-O 11. Re1 h6 12. Bh4 Nh7 13. Bxe7 Qxe7 14. Qa4 Rab8 15. b3 Rb5 $11 {Rublevsky,S-Shirov,A/Poikovsky 2006}) 8. Be3 Qb8 $13 {Rublevsky,S-Ivanchuk,V/Polanica Zdroj 1998}) (7. Re1 e6 8. d3 Nd7 9. Nbd2 Bh5 10. Nf1 Be7 11. Ng3 Bg6 $11 {Ghaem Maghami,E-Akopian,V/Khanty Mansiysk 2007}) 7... Bh5 8. Re1 (8. d3 Nd7 9. Bf4 e5 10. Bh2 Be7 11. Nbd2 O-O 12. Qc2 Bg6 $11 {Boudre,J-Grischuk,A/Montpellier 2006}) 8... e6 9. d3 Be7 10. Nbd2 Nd7 11. Nf1 O-O $11 {Shirov,A-Topalov,V/Prague 2002.}) 6. c3 Nf6 ({Another interesting continuation is} 6... f5 $5 7. exf5 (7. d4 fxe4 8. Ng5 (8. Nxe5 $2 dxe5 9. Qh5+ Kd7 10. dxe5 Kc7 $17 {Yandemirov,V-Sutovsky,E/Saint Vincent 2005}) 8... d5 9. dxe5 Be7 10. f4 g6 11. Qa4 Qb6 12. c4 h6 13. cxd5 hxg5 14. d6 c4+ 15. Kh1 g4 $13 {Miroshnichenko,E-Movsesian,S/Panormo 2002}) 7... Bxf5 8. d4 cxd4 9. cxd4 e4 10. Qc2 Rc8 11. Ng5 Ne7 12. f3 exf3 13. Qb3 Qb6 14. Qf7+ Kd7 15. Nxf3 Be6 16. Qf4 Nd5 17. Qg3 $13 {Ovetchkin,R-Tiviakov,S/Dresden 2007.}) 7. Re1 ({White can again deviate:  a)} 7. d4 cxd4 8. cxd4 exd4 (8... Nxe4 $2 9. Qc2 $16) 9. Nxd4 (9. Qxd4 Qb6 10. Bg5 Qxd4 11. Nxd4 Bd7 12. Bxf6 gxf6 13. Nd2 Rg8 14. Rfd1 c5 15. Ne2 f5 16. Nc3 O-O-O $13 {Korosciel,A-Przezdziecka,M/Poraj 2003}) 9... Bd7 10. Nc3 Be7 11. Bf4 O-O $11 {Komliakov,V-Banikas,H/Yerevan 1996.}) ({b)} 7. Qe2 Bg4 8. h3 Bh5 9. Rd1 Be7 10. d3 Nd7 {½-½ Bobras,P-Zezulkin,J/Poznan 1999.}) ({c)} 7. d3 Be7 8. Re1 O-O 9. Nbd2 Re8 10. Nc4 Be6 11. Qa4 Qc7 $11 {Simonov,S-Sitnikov,D/Novokuznetsk 2008.}) 7... Be7 ({Also possible is} 7... Bg4 8. d4 (8. h3 Bxf3 9. Qxf3 Be7 10. d3 O-O 11. Na3 Ne8 12. Nc4 Nc7 13. b4 cxb4 14. cxb4 Ne6 15. Be3 Bg5 $11 {Svidler,P-Tiviakov,S/Eppingen 2008}) 8... cxd4 9. cxd4 Nd7 10. Be3 Be7 11. Nbd2 exd4 12. Bxd4 O-O 13. Qc2 (13. Nc4 Nb6 14. Ne3 Be6 15. Qc2 c5 16. Bc3 d5 17. exd5 Nxd5 18. Nxd5 Qxd5 19. Re5 Qc6 $13 {Shirov,A-Malakhov,V/Villarrobledo 2008}) 13... Rc8 14. Qc3 Nf6 15. h3 c5 16. hxg4 cxd4 17. Qxd4 Nxg4 18. Nc4 Qc7 19. Rac1 Rfd8 {½-½ Ye Jiangchuan-Ni Hua/Tripoli 2004.}) 8. d4 cxd4 9. cxd4 exd4 (9... Qc7 $5 10. dxe5 dxe5 11. Nbd2 O-O 12. Qc2 Ba6 13. Nc4 Nd7 14. Bd2 f6 15. Rac1 Kh8 16. Nh4 Nc5 17. Re3 Ne6 18. Ba5 Qd7 19. Nf5 c5 20. Qd2 Nd4 21. Rd3 Qe6 22. Nxe7 {½-½ Nevednichy,V-Fercec,N/Bosnjaci 2005.}) 10. Nxd4 ({Bad is} 10. e5 $2 dxe5 11. Nxe5 Qd5 12. Nf3 Bg4 $17 {Nielsen,S-Gasseholm,F/Copenhagen 1993}) ({but White can think of} 10. Qxd4 O-O 11. Bg5 (11. Bf4 c5 12. Qd3 d5 $13) 11... h6 12. Bh4 c5 $13 {Shliperman,I-Timoshenko,G/New York 1999.}) 10... Bd7 11. Nc3 O-O 12. b3 ({An alternative is} 12. Bf4 Re8 (12... d5 13. exd5 Nxd5 14. Nxd5 cxd5 15. Qf3 Bf6 16. Be5 $1 Bxe5 17. Rxe5 $14 {Iordachescu,V-Aronian,L/Bucharest 1999}) (12... Qb6 13. Qd2 Rfe8 14. Rad1 Rad8 15. Bg5 h6 16. Bh4 Qb7 $11 {Tiviakov,S-Noritsyn,N/Ottawa 2007}) 13. Rc1 (13. e5 dxe5 14. Bxe5 Qb6 $11 {Ovetchkin,R-Laxman,R/Internet 2005}) (13. h3 Qb6 14. Qd2 Rad8 15. Rad1 h6 16. Qc2 Bf8 17. Nf3 Be6 $11 {Castellanos Rodriguez,R-Garcia Vasquez,J/Mislata 2007}) 13... Bf8 14. Rc2 Qb6 15. Rd2 c5 16. Nf3 Bc6 $13 {Avdeenko,T-Savina,A/Smolensk 2008.}) 12... Re8 13. Bb2 Bf8 14. Qf3 Qc8 $5 15. h3 Rb8 $1 16. g4 (16. Rad1 c5 17. Nf5 Bxf5 18. exf5 c4 19. Ne2 Nd7 20. f6 g6 $11 {.}) 16... c5 17. Nf5 Bxf5 18. exf5 (18. gxf5 Qc6 19. Re2 Rbc8 20. Kg2 c4 $11 {.}) 18... Qb7 $5 (18... c4 19. Rxe8 Nxe8 20. Nd5 Nc7 21. Bd4 Nxd5 22. Qxd5 cxb3 23. axb3 a6 $11 {.}) 19. Qxb7 Rxb7 20. g5 Rxe1+ 21. Rxe1 Nd7 22. Re8 Rb8 $2 (22... c4 $2 23. Nd5 cxb3 (23... Nb6 24. f6 $18) 24. Ne7+ $1 Kh8 25. f6 $1 g6 26. axb3 Rxb3 27. Bd4 h6 28. h4 hxg5 29. hxg5 $16) (22... f6 $1 23. g6 (23. gxf6 Nxf6 24. Rc8 Kf7 $11) 23... hxg6 24. fxg6 Ne5 25. Ne4 Nxg6 26. Nxd6 Rd7 27. Nc4 Nf4 $11 {.}) 23. Rxb8 Nxb8 24. Kg2 $1 $16 (24. Nd5 $2 Nd7 25. Kg2 Nb6 26. Nxb6 axb6 27. Kf3 d5 $11 {.}) 24... Be7 25. f4 Kf8 26. Kf3 Ke8 27. Ke4 g6 28. Nd5 Nc6 29. h4 Bd8 30. Bc3 Kf8 (30... Kd7 31. fxg6 hxg6 32. f5 $16 {.}) 31. b4 $2 (31. f6 Ke8 32. f5 Kd7 33. h5 gxh5 34. g6 fxg6 35. fxg6 hxg6 36. f7 Be7 37. Bg7 Ke6 38. Nxe7 Kxf7 39. Nxc6 Kxg7 40. Nxa7 $18 {.}) 31... cxb4 32. Bxb4 (32. Nxb4 Ne7 33. fxg6 fxg6 $11 {.}) 32... Nxb4 33. Nxb4 Bb6 34. Nd5 (34. Nd3 Ke7 $11 {.}) 34... Bf2 35. Nf6 h5 $2 (35... Bxh4 36. Nxh7+ Ke8 37. Kd5 Bg3 $11 {.}) 36. gxh6 Bxh4 37. Nh7+ $1 Ke7 $2 (37... Kg8 38. Ng5 gxf5+ 39. Kxf5 d5 40. h7+ Kg7 41. Nxf7 Kxh7 42. Ne5 $16 {.}) 38. f6+ $1 $18 (38. Ng5 $2 Kf6 39. fxg6 Kxg6 (39... fxg6 40. Kd5 $18) 40. h7 Kg7 41. Nxf7 Kxh7 42. Nxd6 $16 {.}) 38... Bxf6 39. Nxf6 Kxf6 40. Kd5 g5 41. fxg5+ Kg6 42. Kxd6 f6 43. h7 1-0


