1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 Bb4+ 4. Nbd2 O-O ({The early} 4... Nc6 5. a3 $1 ({looks OK. White can also choose} 5. g3 d5 $5 6. Bg2 (6. Qc2 dxc4 7. Qxc4 Qd5 $11) 6... dxc4 7. O-O {accepting an interesting gambit, as in Haba,P-Strauss,A/Vienna 1998 but the text move is more positional:}) 5... Bxd2+ (5... Be7 $6 6. e4 ({or simply} 6. g3 {transposing}) 6... d5 7. cxd5 exd5 8. e5 Ne4 9. Bd3 Bf5 10. Qc2 Bg6 11. O-O $16) 6. Qxd2 ({Of course} 6. Bxd2 {is possible:} Ne4 (6... d6 7. Qc2 e5 8. d5 Ne7 9. e4 O-O 10. Be2 Ne8 11. O-O f5 12. exf5 Bxf5 13. Qb3 $14 {Volke,K-Votava,J/Germany 1998}) 7. e3 O-O 8. Rc1 d6 9. b4 Ne7 10. Bd3 f5 11. Qc2 Nxd2 12. Qxd2 Ng6 13. c5 $14 {Podgaets,M-Kornilov,P/Odessa 2007}) 6... O-O 7. b4 Ne4 (7... d6 8. Bb2 Qe7 9. e3 $14 {Cheng,B-Fan,B/Kitchener 2006}) 8. Qc2 f5 9. g3 d6 10. Bb2 $14 {Hohrmann,J-Waechtler,F/Porz 1991.}) 5. g3 d5 ({Black's alternatives are: a)} 5... Re8 6. Bg2 d5 7. O-O Nc6 (7... c6 8. Qc2 Nbd7 9. e4 dxe4 10. Nxe4 Nxe4 11. Qxe4 c5 12. a3 Ba5 13. Rd1 cxd4 14. Nxd4 $16 {Clavijo,J-Gonzalez Manchon,J/Columbia 1990}) 8. Qc2 e5 9. cxd5 Nxd5 $6 (9... Nxd4 10. Nxd4 exd4 11. Nb3 Nxd5 12. Nxd4 $14) 10. dxe5 Bg4 11. Rd1 $16 {Loginov,A-Khruschiov,A/Moscow 2007.}) ({b)} 5... Ne4 6. Bg2 d5 (6... f5 7. O-O Bxd2 (7... Nxd2 8. Bxd2 Bxd2 9. Qxd2 d6 10. Rfe1 Nd7 11. e4 $16 {Pessi,J-Peltola,L/Helsinki 1999}) 8. Nxd2 Nxd2 9. Bxd2 $16 {Roods,S-Bono,G/Las Vegas 1996}) (6... c5 7. O-O Bxd2 8. Bxd2 Qe7 9. Be3 $16 {Grivas,E-Ratcu,T/Internet 2000}) (6... Nxd2 7. Bxd2 Qe7 8. O-O Bxd2 9. Qxd2 d6 10. Qc3 (10. Rac1 e5 11. c5 Nc6 12. d5 $16 {Bogdanov,V-Schulz,M/Bad Wiessee 2006}) 10... Re8 11. Rac1 c6 (11... e5 12. c5 exd4 13. Nxd4 dxc5 14. Qxc5 Qxc5 15. Rxc5 Na6 16. Ra5 $16) 12. c5 dxc5 13. dxc5 e5 14. Nd2 Na6 15. Ne4 $16 {Roelvaag,M-Esbensen,A/Vadso 2007}) 7. O-O Nc6 8. Qc2 f5 (8... Nxd2 9. Bxd2 Bxd2 10. Qxd2 Ne7 (10... dxc4 11. Rfc1 $14) 11. Rac1 c6 12. Rfd1 Nf5 13. Qc2 Nd6 14. Nd2 f5 15. e3 $14 {Sherwin,J-Evans Quek,D/Monmouth 2004}) 9. e3 (9. Nb3 Be7 10. cxd5 exd5 11. Rd1 Bf6 12. Bf4 g5 13. Be5 $13 {Halkias,S-Papaioannou,I/Kavala 1995}) 9... Be7 (9... a5 10. a3 Bxd2 11. Nxd2 $14 {Marszalek,R-Vasiukov,E/Leningrad 1974}) 10. a3 a5 (10... Qe8 11. b4 Bd7 12. Nb3 a6 13. cxd5 exd5 14. Nc5 $14 {Petrzela,P-Balazec,L/Moravia 2003}) 11. b3 (11. Ne1 Bf6 12. Nd3 Qe8 13. Nf3 b6 14. cxd5 exd5 15. Nf4 $14 {Bouwmeester,H-Pirc,V/Munich 1954}) 11... Qe8 12. Bb2 Qh5 13. Nxe4 fxe4 14. Nd2 Rf6 15. Qd1 Qxd1 16. Raxd1 $14 {Lesiege,A-Pineault,D/Montreal 1997.}) ({c)} 5... c5 6. Bg2 (6. dxc5 Na6 (6... Bxc5 7. Bg2 Bxf2+ $2 (7... Nc6 {transposes}) 8. Kxf2 Ng4+ 9. Ke1 Qb6 (9... Ne3 10. Qb3 Nxg2+ 11. Kf2 $18) 10. c5 Qxc5 11. Ne4 Qb4+ 12. Nc3 $18 {Santos,A-Pinheiro,A/Barreiro 2000}) 7. Bg2 Nxc5 8. O-O b6 9. a3 Bxd2 10. Bxd2 Bb7 11. Be3 $14 {Fominyh,A-Nielsen,P/Katowice 1993}) 6... cxd4 (6... Nc6 7. dxc5 Bxc5 {transposes} 8. O-O d5 (8... b6 9. Nb3 Be7 10. Bf4 (10. Nfd4 Bb7 11. Nxc6 Bxc6 12. Bxc6 dxc6 13. Bf4 Qc8 14. Qc2 Rd8 $11 {Porat,D-Egeland,M/Port Erin 2003}) 10... Bb7 11. Bd6 (11. Rc1 Ne4 12. Qc2 Nb4 13. Qb1 $14 {Martins,G-Verissimo,F/Fortaleza 1998}) 11... Rc8 12. Rc1 Ne4 13. Bxe7 Qxe7 14. Nfd2 $14) 9. cxd5 (9. Nb3 Be7 10. Nbd4 Nxd4 11. Qxd4 b6 12. Ne5 $14 {Gessat,M-Sondors,P/Germany 1985}) (9. a3 a5 10. cxd5 exd5 11. Nb3 Bb6 12. Nbd4 $14 {Najdorf,M-Merlo,C/Buenos Aires 1960}) 9... exd5 (9... Nxd5 10. Nc4 (10. Nb3 Be7 11. Nfd4 Nxd4 12. Nxd4 Bf6 13. Nb3 a5 14. a4 Qe7 15. e4 Nb4 16. Qe2 e5 $11 {Kefalis,H-Pandavos,E/Ikaria 1998}) 10... Qe7 11. Qb3 $14) (9... Qxd5 10. Nb3 Bb6 11. Nfd4 Ne4 12. Be3 $14) 10. Nb3 Bb6 11. Bf4 Re8 12. Rc1 $14 {Harikrishna,P-Georgiev,K/Bled 2002}) 7. Nxd4 Nc6 8. Nc2 Be7 9. O-O d5 (9... a6 10. b3 b5 11. Nd4 Qb6 12. Nxc6 dxc6 13. Ne4 bxc4 14. bxc4 Rd8 15. Qc2 Ra7 16. Rb1 Qc7 17. c5 $14 {Alburt,L-Short,N/Foxboro 1985}) (9... b6 10. b3 Bb7 11. Bb2 d6 12. e4 (12. e3 Qc7 13. Qe2 a6 14. Rac1 Nb8 15. e4 Nbd7 16. Nd4 Rfe8 17. Rfd1 $14 {Zhang Zhong-Rott,G/Dos Hermanas 2004}) 12... Qc7 13. Qe2 a6 14. Ne3 $14) (9... d6 10. b3 Qc7 11. Bb2 b6 12. e4 Bb7 13. Qe2 Rad8 14. Ne3 Rfe8 15. Rac1 Qb8 16. f4 $14 {Johansen,A-Aubert,C/Gausdal 2003}) (9... Rb8 10. b3 b5 11. Bb2 $14 {Jablonicky,F-Lisko,F/Slovakia 2006}) 10. cxd5 Nxd5 (10... exd5 11. Nb3 Bf5 12. Ncd4 Bg6 (12... Be4 13. f3 (13. Bxe4 $5 Nxe4 14. Be3 $14) 13... Bg6 14. Nxc6 bxc6 15. Be3 Re8 16. Rc1 Qd7 17. Qd2 Rab8 18. Nc5 Bxc5 19. Bxc5 Qe6 20. Rfe1 $14 {Buhmann,R-Nikolaidis,I/Fuerth 2002}) 13. Bf4 Rc8 14. Rc1 $14 {Viladiu Martinez,J-Barroso Martinez,F/Spain 1997}) 11. Nc4 Qc7 {(½-½ Blagojevic,D-Kovacevic,A/Budva 2002)} 12. N2e3 (12. e4 Nb6 13. Qe2 Nxc4 14. Qxc4 Bd7 15. Be3 Rfc8 16. Rfd1 Ne5 17. Qxc7 Rxc7 18. Ne1 Ng4 {½-½ Remon,A-Vilela,J/Bayamo 1980}) 12... Nf6 13. Bd2 Rd8 14. Rc1 Bd7 15. Na5 $14 {.}) ({d)} 5... d6 6. Bg2 Re8 (6... Qe7 7. O-O Bxd2 8. Qxd2 e5 9. b3 e4 (9... Re8 10. dxe5 dxe5 11. Bb2 Nc6 12. Rad1 $14 {Browne,W-Goldin,A/Los Angeles 1991}) 10. Ne1 d5 11. Nc2 Rd8 12. Ba3 Qe8 13. f3 $14 {Tarjan,J-Kurajica,B/Indonesia 1983}) 7. O-O e5 8. Nb3 e4 (8... exd4 9. Nfxd4 Nbd7 10. a3 Bc5 11. Nxc5 Nxc5 12. b4 Ne6 13. Bb2 $14 {Erdos,V-Susak,Z/Sibenik 2007}) 9. a3 exf3 10. Bxf3 Bxa3 11. Rxa3 $14 {Carlsen,M-Morozevich,A/Monte Carlo 2007.}) 6. Qc2 (6. Bg2 {is a possible and 'must' continuation in my opinion:} {a)} c5 ({b)} 6... dxc4 7. Qc2 Nc6 (7... b5 8. a4 bxa4 (8... c6 9. axb5 cxb5 10. Ng5 $16) 9. O-O Bb7 10. Nxc4 Nbd7 11. Rxa4 a5 12. Bd2 $14 {Gelfand,B-Almasi,Z/Monte Carlo 2003}) (7... Qd5 8. O-O Nc6 9. Nxc4 Qf5 (9... Nxd4 10. Nxd4 Qxd4 11. Rd1 Qg4 12. a3 Be7 13. Ne5 $16) 10. Qxf5 exf5 11. Nce5 $14) 8. Qxc4 Ne4 (8... Qd5 9. O-O Bxd2 10. Qxd5 exd5 11. Bxd2 Re8 12. Rfe1 Nd8 13. Ne5 c6 14. f3 Nd7 15. Nd3 Ne6 16. Bc3 f5 17. Kf2 $14 {Carlsen,M-Aronian,L/Monte Carlo 2007}) 9. Qd3 Nxd2 10. Bxd2 Qe7 11. O-O Rd8 12. Bxb4 Nxb4 13. Qc4 Nd5 14. Rac1 c6 15. Rfd1 $14 {Carlsen,M-Stubberud,O/Tromsoe 2007.}) ({c)} 6... b6 7. O-O Bb7 8. cxd5 {transposes to 4...b6.}) 7. cxd5 (7. a3 Bxd2+ 8. Qxd2 Nc6 9. cxd5 Qxd5 10. dxc5 Qxc5 11. b4 $14 {Bareev,E-Vyzmanavin,A/Irkutsk 1986}) 7... Qxd5 8. a3 Bxd2+ 9. Qxd2 cxd4 10. Qxd4 Nc6 (10... Qb5 11. a4 Qf5 12. Ne5 Nbd7 13. Bf4 Nxe5 14. Qxe5 $16 {Fominyh,A-Kunte,A/Mumbai 2004}) 11. Qxd5 Nxd5 12. O-O Rd8 13. Rd1 Bd7 14. Bd2 $14 {Kozul,Z-Pandurevic,M/Zadar 2003.}) 6... c5 $1 (6... b6 7. Bg2 Bb7 8. O-O Nbd7 9. a3 Bd6 (9... Be7 10. b4 (10. cxd5 {seems to be the correct move order}) 10... c5 11. cxd5 Bxd5 (11... exd5 12. bxc5 bxc5 13. dxc5 Nxc5 14. Nd4 Rc8 15. Bh3 Ne6 16. Qd3 Nxd4 17. Qxd4 Bc5 18. Qb2 Rb8 19. Nb3 Ba6 20. Qc2 $14 {Murdzia,P-Sosnicki,M/Krakow 1999}) 12. e4 Bb7 $11 {Gurevich,D-Anka,E/Las Vegas 2001}) 10. b4 c5 11. cxd5 exd5 (11... Nxd5 12. bxc5 bxc5 13. Nc4 Be7 14. Rb1 Ba6 15. Ne3 $14) 12. bxc5 bxc5 13. dxc5 Nxc5 14. Bb2 $14 {Gross,S-Ortel,E/Zamardi 1979.}) 7. Bg2 $2 ({I think that Black gets fine play after the text-move. White should try instead: a)} 7. dxc5 Bxc5 8. Bg2 Nc6 (8... Ng4 9. e3 Nc6 10. O-O Bxe3 11. cxd5 exd5 12. fxe3 Nxe3 13. Qb3 Nxf1 14. Nxf1 d4 15. Bf4 Qb6 16. Qxb6 axb6 17. a3 $14 {Kopylov,M-Meister,Y/Travemuende 2004}) (8... Qb6 9. O-O Ng4 10. e3 Bxe3 11. fxe3 Nxe3 12. Qb3 (12. Qd3 Nxf1+ (12... dxc4 13. Nxc4 Nxc4+ 14. Kh1 Qc7 15. Ng5 g6 16. Rxf7 Rxf7 17. Nxf7 Kxf7 18. Bh6 Nd7 19. Rc1 $16 {Berkvens,J-Dranov,A/Germany 2006}) 13. Kxf1 Nc6 14. Ng5 g6 $13 {Peek,M-Timman,J/Netherlands 2005}) 12... Nxf1+ 13. Qxb6 axb6 14. Bxf1 $14 {Obukhov,A-Janov,D/Novosibirsk 2002}) 9. O-O d4 10. Nb3 Be7 11. Rd1 e5 12. e3 (12. a3 Qc7 13. Nh4 Re8 14. f4 Ng4 $1 $15 {Bilo,H-Busch,R/Brackwede 1974}) 12... Bg4 13. exd4 e4 14. Ng5 (14. d5 $2 Nb4 15. Qc3 exf3 $19 {Dolezal,M-Wians,C/Luxembourg 1990}) 14... Bxd1 15. Qxd1 a5 16. a4 Re8 17. Nxe4 (17. d5 $5 Ne5 18. Qd4 Nd3 19. Nxe4 $44) 17... Nxe4 18. Bxe4 Bf6 19. Bd5 $44 {Topalov,V-Carlsen,M/Nice 2008.}) ({b)} 7. a3 Bxd2+ 8. Bxd2 cxd4 9. Nxd4 dxc4 10. Qxc4 e5 $13 {Toth,B-Cappello,R/Rome 1979.}) 7... cxd4 8. Nxd4 e5 $1 9. N4b3 (9. Nb5 d4 10. O-O a6 11. Na3 Nc6 $15 {.}) 9... Bg4 $2 ({After} 9... Qc7 $1 {Black is more than fine:} 10. O-O Be6 11. a3 Be7 12. Qc3 (12. Nf3 dxc4 13. Ng5 Bg4 14. h3 Bh5 15. Bd2 Nbd7 $17 {Tosic,M-Giorgadze,G/Belgrade 1992}) 12... Nc6 13. cxd5 Nxd5 $17 {.}) ({Unclear is} 9... a5 $6 10. a3 Be7 11. cxd5 (11. Nf3 $6 a4 12. Nbd2 e4 13. Nd4 Bc5 $17 {Lock,G-Corkett,A/Guernsey 2001}) 11... Nxd5 12. O-O Nc6 13. Nf3 {.}) 10. cxd5 Nxd5 11. a3 Be7 12. Nc4 $1 Be6 $5 (12... Nc6 13. O-O Be6 14. Rd1 $14 {.}) 13. Nxe5 Bf6 $44 14. Nd3 Na6 15. O-O Rc8 16. Qd1 Qb6 17. Bd2 $1 Rfe8 $6 (17... Nc3 18. Bxc3 Bxc3 19. bxc3 Bxb3 20. Qd2 $16) (17... Qb5 $5 18. a4 Qd7 19. Qb1 Rfd8 $44 {.}) 18. Nbc1 Ne7 19. Rb1 Ng6 20. Be3 Qb5 (20... Qc7 21. Nb3 Ne5 22. Nd4 $16 {.}) 21. Bxa7 h5 $6 (21... b6 22. a4 Qa5 23. b4 Nxb4 24. Bxb6 Qxb6 25. Rxb4 $14 {.}) 22. a4 Qd7 23. Be3 $16 b5 24. axb5 Qxb5 25. Ra1 Rc4 26. Bd2 h4 27. Ra5 Qb6 28. Ra4 hxg3 29. hxg3 Nc5 30. Nxc5 Qxc5 31. Nd3 Qb5 32. Ra5 Qb6 33. b4 Bg4 34. Ra8 $6 (34. Re1 $16 {.}) 34... Rxa8 35. Bxa8 Bd4 36. Bg2 Qd6 37. Qb3 $2 (37. Qa4 $1 $16 {.}) 37... Be6 38. Qa3 Qxg3 $1 39. e3 Qg5 $2 (39... Qd6 $1 40. exd4 Rxd4 41. Qa8+ Kh7 42. Qc6 Qxc6 43. Bxc6 Rxd3 44. Be3 Rb3 $11 {.}) 40. f4 Qg3 $6 (40... Qf5 41. exd4 Rxd4 42. Rf3 Bc4 43. Ne5 $1 $16 {.}) 41. Rf3 $18 Qg4 42. Nf2 Qf5 43. exd4 Nh4 44. Rg3 Qc2 45. Be3 Qe2 46. Qa5 Nxg2 47. Kxg2 Rc3 48. Qe5 g6 49. f5 $1 Bxf5 50. Qe8+ 1-0


