1. Nf3 g6 2. e4 d6 3. d4 Nf6 4. Nc3 Bg7 5. Be3 O-O 6. Qd2 a6 7. Bh6 c5 (7... b5) 8. Bxg7 Kxg7 9. dxc5 (9. O-O-O Nc6 10. dxc5 dxc5 11. Qe3 (11. Qxd8 Rxd8 12. Rxd8 Nxd8 13. e5 Nd7 14. Be2 Nc6) 11... Qa5 12. h3 Be6 13. e5 Ne8 14. h4 h5 15. a3 Nc7 16. Bd3 Nb5) 9... dxc5 10. Qxd8 (10. O-O-O Qxd2+ 11. Rxd2 Nc6 (11... b5) 12. e5 Ng4 13. Re2 Nd4 14. Nxd4 cxd4 15. Na4 Be6) 10... Rxd8 11. e5 Nfd7 (11... Nh5 12. Na4 Nc6 13. Nxc5 Nb4 14. Bd3 {Kurajica,B-Mujic,H/Neum 2000} Nf4 15. O-O Nfxd3 16. cxd3 $11 Bg4) 12. O-O-O Nc6 13. Bc4 Nb6 (13... b5 14. Bd5 Bb7 15. Rhe1 (15. e6 Nf6 16. exf7 Nxd5 (16... b4 17. Ng5) 17. Nxd5 Nd4 18. Nxd4 Bxd5 $13 {Guliev,S-Kondenko,A/Yalta 1996. Black should keep a flexible centre.}) 15... Nb6) 14. Rxd8 Nxd8 15. Rd1 (15. Bd3 Be6 16. Be4 $14 {Preferable is} Rc8 17. Rd1) 15... Bd7 (15... Bg4 16. Be2 Nc6 17. h3 Bf5 18. g4 Be6 19. Ng5 Nxe5 $11 {Not that difficult is} 20. Nxe6+ fxe6 21. Re1 Nd5 22. Nxd5 $16 {Clearly better is} exd5 23. Bxa6 Rxa6 24. Rxe5 e6) 16. Ng5 (16. Bd5 Rc8 17. Be4 Bc6 $19 {White should concentrate on drawing the game:} 18. g3) 16... Bc6 17. Bf1 h6 18. Nge4 Ne6 19. g3 f5 20. exf6+ exf6 21. a4 f5 (21... Nxa4 22. Nxa4 Bxa4 23. Bc4 Bc6 24. Bxe6 (24. Re1 $15 f5 $15 {Black loses his way in the last moves. Still winning is} 25. Nd6 Nd8 26. Ne8+ Kf8 27. Nf6 $19 Nf7 $19 28. Nh7+ $19 {A better try is} Kg7 29. Re7 Kxh7 30. Bxf7 Kg7 31. Bd5+ Kf8 32. Rf7+ Ke8 $17 {Returning the favour. Winning was} 33. Rh7) 24... Bxe4 25. Rd7+ {0-1 (67) Logothetis,S (2095)-Grivas,E (2510) Athens 1997 CBM 122 [Grivas,Efstratios]} {The final mistake. White should have played} Kh8 26. Bd5) 22. a5 Nd7 23. Nd6 Ne5 (23... Nf6 24. Re1) (23... Rd8 24. Bc4 Nd4 (24... Ndf8 25. f4 Nd4 26. Nf7) 25. b4 Ne5 26. bxc5 Nxc4 27. Nxc4) 24. f4 Ng4 (24... Nf7 25. Nxf7 Kxf7 26. Bc4) 25. Nxb7 Ne3 26. Re1 Nxf1 27. Rxe6 Bxb7 28. Re7+ Kg8 29. Rxb7 Nxh2 30. Nd5 Nf1 31. Nc7 Rf8 32. Nxa6 Nxg3 33. Nxc5 h5 34. a6 h4 35. a7 h3 36. Nd3 (36. Rb8 h2 37. Rxf8+ Kxf8 38. a8=Q+ Kf7 39. Qb7+ Kg8 40. b4 h1=Q+ 41. Qxh1 Nxh1 $2 42. b5) 36... Ne4 37. Rb8 h2 38. Rxf8+ Kxf8 39. a8=Q+ Kg7 40. Qxe4 fxe4 41. Nf2 e3 42. Nh1 Kf6 $2 43. b4 Kf5 44. b5 Kxf4 45. b6 Kf3 46. b7 Kg2 47. b8=Q Kxh1 48. Qg3 0-1


