+ Ke6 51. a4 (51. Kxf2 Nc3) 51... c3 52. Kxf2 Nb4 53. Ke2 d5 54. g7 Kf7 55. Be7 (55. Bf6 d4 56. a5) 55... Na6 (55... d4 56. Bxc5 d3+ 57. Kd1) 56. Bf6 d4 57. Kd3 Nb4+ 58. Kc4 c2 59. Bg5 Na2 60. a5) 49. Kxf2 Nb6 50. g6 Nxd5 51. g7 Kf7 52. Bxd6 $11 {This position can arise with either 6.Be3 or 6.Bg5} c4 $5 53. Bf8 b4 (53... Nc7 $11 54. Kf3 Ne6 55. Bb4 Nxg7 56. Ke4 (56. Kf4) 56... Ke6 $18 57. Be1 (57. Kf4 Nf5 58. Be1 Nd4) 57... Nf5 58. a3 Kf6 59. Kf4 (59. Kd5 Kg5 60. Kc5 Nxg3 61. Kxb5 (61. Bxg3 c3 $18 {De Leeuw,R-Westra,B/Netherlands 1996} 62. Be1 (62. Be5 c2 63. Bb2 h4 $14 {Olafsson,H-Brunner,L/Manila OL 1992}) 62... c2 63. Bd2+ Kg4 64. Kd4 Kf3) 61... h4 62. a4 (62. Kxc4 $2 Kg4 $1 63. Bf2 Kf3 64. Bg1 Kg2) 62... c3 $16) 59... Kg6 60. Bd2 Nd4) 54. Ke1 b3 55. axb3 $13 cxb3 56. Kd2 Ne3 57. Kc3 Nf5 58. Kxb3 Nxg3 59. Kc2 h4 60. Bd6 Kxg7 $1 61. Kd1 Kg6 62. Bxg3 0-1


