1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. e4 d6 5. d4 O-O 6. Be2 e5 7. O-O Qe8 (7... Nc6 8. d5 Ne7 9. b4) 8. dxe5 (8. d5 Nfd7 (8... a5 9. Ne1 (9. Bg5 h6 10. Bh4 Na6) 9... Na6 10. Nd3 Nd7 11. Be3 f5 12. f3 Ndc5 (12... f4 13. Bf2 $14 g5 $6 14. a3) 13. b3 Bd7 $14 {Cramling,P-Gullaksen,E/Catalan Bay 2003} {Black's options are: a)} 14. Rb1 $6 b6 15. a3 Nxd3 16. Bxd3 Nc5 17. Bc2 f4 18. Bf2 g5 $16 19. b4 $6 axb4 20. axb4 Na4 21. Nxa4 Bxa4 22. Bxa4 Rxa4 $13 {Mikhalchishin,A-Weindl,A/Bern 1996} 23. c5) 9. Ne1 f5 10. Nd3 Nf6 11. f3 $16 f4 12. c5 Rf7 13. cxd6 cxd6 14. Nf2 Bf8 15. Bd2 h5 16. a4 g5 17. h3 Rg7 18. Nb5 Na6 19. Rc1 Qg6 20. Rc4 g4 $2 21. fxg4 {1-0 Cramling,P-Tegzes,L/Richmond 2004} {Black can consider} hxg4 22. Bxg4 Nxg4 23. Nxg4 Nc5) (8. Re1 exd4 9. Nxd4 Nxe4 $16 {Arsovic,G-Ilincic,Z/Ulcinj 1997} {b)} 10. Nxe4 Qxe4 11. Be3 Qh4 $1 12. Nb5 Qd8 13. Qd2 Nc6) 8... dxe5 9. b4 (9. Be3 $16 {This is too risky, as the black e-pawn will soon become a target.} Nbd7 $14 {is preferable} (9... b6) {Possible is} 10. h3 (10. Nd2 c6 11. b4 Qe7 12. c5 Rd8 {1-0 Makarov,M-Loskutov,O/Tomsk 1998} 13. Qc1 {did not prove a success:} Nf8 14. Nc4 Ne6 15. Nd6 Nd4) 10... Qe7 (10... c6 11. Qd6) 11. Nd5 Qd8 12. Qc2 Nh5 13. Bg5 f6 14. Be3 c6 $14 15. Nc3 $2 Nf4) 9... Qe7 (9... Bg4 10. b5 Bxf3 11. Bxf3 Qe6 12. Nd5 Rc8 13. Nxf6+ (13. Be3 Nbd7 $16 {A blunder. Not that difficult was} 14. c5 Bf8 15. Nxf6+ $1 $18 {Or} Nxf6 16. a4 c6) 13... Qxf6 14. Be3 Rd8 (14... h5 15. Rb1 Bf8 16. Rb3) 15. Qc1 Qe7 16. c5 c6 17. a4 $1 Nd7 (17... a6 18. b6 {Black returns the favour. With} Nd7 19. Qc4 h5 $14 {he could keep White's advantage to the minimum} 20. Rfd1 Nf8) 18. bxc6 bxc6 19. Qc4 h5 20. Rab1 Nf8 21. Qa6 Ne6 22. Rb7 Rd7 (22... Nxc5 23. Rxe7 Nxa6 24. Rd1) 23. Rfb1) 10. b5 (10. Nd5 Nxd5 (10... Qd8) 11. cxd5 Qxb4 12. Qd3 Qd6 13. Ba3 c5 14. dxc6 Qxd3 $2 15. Bxd3 $1 {Now it's all over.} Rd8) 10... a6 (10... c6 11. a4 Rd8 12. Qc2 Bg4 13. Ba3 (13. a5) 13... Qe8 (13... Qc7 $1) 14. a5 Bxf3 15. Bxf3 Bf8 $2) (10... Nbd7 11. a4 $1 Nc5 12. Ba3 $1 b6) 11. a4 axb5 (11... Nbd7 12. Ba3 Nc5 13. a5) 12. cxb5 Rd8 $6 13. Qc2 Nbd7 (13... Bg4 14. a5 c6 $16 15. a6 cxb5 16. a7 Na6 17. Nxb5) 14. Ba3 Qe8 15. Rfd1 Bf8 16. Bxf8 Nxf8 (16... Qxf8 17. Nd5 Nxd5 18. Rxd5) 17. Rxd8 Qxd8 18. Nxe5 Qd4 19. Nf3 Qc5 20. Qb2 $1 Ng4 21. Nd1 Nd7 22. Rc1 $1 Qb6 23. Nd2 Nc5 (23... Ngf6 24. Ne3 Rxa4 25. e5) 24. Nc4 Qf6 25. Bxg4 (25. Bxg4 Qxb2 26. Ncxb2 Nb3 27. Bxc8) 1-0


