1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 c6 3. Nf3 d5 4. Nc3 a6 5. a4 e6 (5... Bf5 $6 6. Qb3 $14) (5... g6) 6. e3 (6. g3 dxc4 (6... b6 7. Bg2 Bb7 8. O-O Be7 9. Ne5 Nbd7 10. Nxd7 Nxd7 11. e4 $1 $14 {Kramnik,V-Bareev,E/Belgrade/1993/1:0/(40)/}) (6... c5 7. cxd5 exd5 8. Bg5 Be6 9. Bg2 Nc6 10. O-O Be7 11. dxc5 Bxc5 12. Rc1 $14 {Van Wely,L-Tregubov,P/Wijk aan Zee/1995/1:0/(39)/}) (6... Nbd7 7. Bg2 Bb4 $1 8. O-O O-O 9. Qb3 a5 10. Rd1 b6 $13 {Cifuentes Parada,R-Dreev,A/Wijk aan Zee/1995/0:1/(33)/}) 7. Bg2 c5 8. O-O (8. dxc5 Qxd1+ 9. Nxd1 Nc6 10. Ne3 Bxc5 11. Nxc4 Ke7 12. O-O Nd5 $1 $10 {Bareev,E-Shirov,A/Groningen/1993/0,5/(22)/}) 8... cxd4 9. Nxd4 Bc5 10. Be3 Qe7 11. Nc2 O-O $10 {Kamsky,G-Bareev,E/Linares/1994/0,5/(45)/}) (6. Bg5 $5) (6. a5 $5) 6... c5 $1 (6... Nbd7) 7. cxd5 (7. Bd3 Nc6 8. O-O Be7 9. cxd5 exd5 10. dxc5 Bg4 11. h3 Bh5 12. b3 Bxc5 13. Bb2 O-O 14. g4 Bg6 15. Bxg6 hxg6 16. g5 Ne4 17. Qxd5 Nxc3 18. Qxc5 Ne4 19. Qc4 Nxg5 20. Nxg5 Qxg5+ 21. Kh2 Rad8 $10 {Belov,I-Dreev,A/Moscow/1985/0,5/38/}) (7. Be2 Nc6 8. O-O Bd6 9. b3 O-O 10. Bb2 $10) 7... exd5 8. Be2 Nc6 9. O-O Bd6 10. b3 (10. dxc5 $5 Bxc5 11. b3 O-O 12. Bb2 $10) 10... cxd4 11. Nxd4 Qc7 12. Nf3 Be6 13. Ba3 (13. Bb2 O-O 14. Rc1 $10) 13... Bxa3 14. Rxa3 O-O $15 {×b4/} 15. Nd4 (15. Ra1 $5 Rac8 16. Rc1 $15) 15... Rac8 16. Nxc6 Qxc6 17. b4 Ne4 18. Nb1 (18. Nxe4 $6 dxe4 $17 {c,d/}) (18. Na2 Qc2 $5 19. Qxc2 (19. Bd3 $2 Qb2 $19) 19... Rxc2 20. Bd3 Rb2 21. a5 Rc8 $15) 18... Qb6 (18... Qc2 $6 19. Bd3) 19. b5 a5 (19... axb5 20. Bxb5 (20. axb5 Rc5 $15) 20... Nd6 21. Bd3 Nc4 22. Rc3 $15) 20. Rd3 Rc5 21. Rd4 Rfc8 22. Bd3 Qc7 (22... f5 23. f3 Nd6 24. Nd2 Nc4 25. Qe2 $15) 23. Nd2 Rc1 (23... f5 24. Nb3 Rc3 25. f3 $132 { e1/}) 24. Qe2 f5 25. f3 $2 (25. Rxc1 $1 Qxc1+ 26. Nf1 b6 27. f3 Nc3 28. Qd2 Qa1 (28... Qxd2 29. Nxd2 Nd1 30. e4 $13) 29. Bc2 $15) 25... Nc3 26. Qf2 Nd1 $1 $17 27. Qe2 Qe5 $1 {× e3/} 28. Nb3 Nxe3 29. Rxc1 Rxc1+ 30. Nxc1 Qxd4 31. Nb3 Qb6 32. Kh1 d4 $19 33. Qb2 Bxb3 34. Qxb3+ Kf8 35. h3 g6 36. Bb1 Qc7 37. Qe6 (37. Qb2 Qc3 $19) 37... Qc1+ 38. Kh2 Nf1+ (38... Qxb1 $4 39. Qf6+ $10) 39. Kg1 Qe3+ 40. Qxe3 Nxe3 41. Kf2 Ke7 { d6-c5-b4 ×a4,g2/} 0-1


