1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Nf3 O-O 5. g3 d6 6. Bg2 Nc6 7. O-O Bf5 8. Ne1 Qd7 9. e4 Bh3 10. Nc2 Bxg2 11. Kxg2 e5 12. d5 Ne7 13. f4 exf4 14. gxf4 {(D) } Rae8 15. Qf3 Kh8 $6 (15... Nh5 {is the main alternative move. White should try} 16. f5 Nc8 17. Bg5 h6 18. Be3 Nb6 $13) 16. Be3 Nh5 17. Bd4 Ng8 18. Rae1 Re7 19. Bxg7+ Nxg7 20. Qf2 c5 21. Kh1 Rfe8 {Black's plan to put pressure on the white e4-pawn was not the best.} 22. e5 $5 b6 (22... dxe5 23. fxe5 Rxe5 24. Rxe5 Rxe5 25. Qxf7 $16) 23. b4 $1 Nf5 $5 (23... dxe5 24. bxc5 bxc5 25. fxe5 Rxe5 26. Rxe5 Rxe5 27. Qxf7 Qh3 28. Qf3 $14) 24. bxc5 bxc5 25. exd6 $2 ({Much better was} 25. Ne3 Nd4 $1 (25... Nxe3 26. Rxe3 dxe5 27. Ne4 exf4 28. Nxc5 Qf5 29. Rxe7 Rxe7 30. d6 Re8 31. d7 Rd8 32. Qd4+ Qf6 33. Rxf4 Qxd4 34. Rxd4 Nf6 35. Rd6 Kg7 36. Kg1 $18) (25... dxe5 26. Nxf5 Qxf5 27. d6 Rd7 28. Qxc5 e4 29. Qxf5 gxf5 30. c5 $16) 26. Ne4 dxe5 27. Nxc5 (27. fxe5 Rxe5 28. Nxc5 Qe7 29. Nc2 Nxc2 30. Rxe5 Qxe5 31. Qxc2 Rc8 $13) 27... Qc7 28. Nd3 exf4 29. Nxf4 $14) 25... Qxd6 26. Rxe7 Rxe7 27. Re1 Nf6 28. Nb5 (28. Rxe7 Qxe7 29. Qe1 Qd6 $15) 28... Rxe1+ 29. Nxe1 Qe7 $17 {Now the white pawn-structure is very weak and Black's pieces too active.} 30. Nc3 (30. Ng2 Qe4 31. Qxc5 Nh4 32. Qg1 Nxg2 33. Qxg2 Qxc4 34. Nxa7 Nxd5 $17) 30... Ne4 $1 31. Qb2 Nd4 32. Nb5 (32. Nxe4 Qxe4+ 33. Ng2 h5 $17) 32... Nf6 $2 (32... Qh4 33. Ng2 Qg4 34. Qa1 Nf2+ 35. Kg1 Nh3+ 36. Kh1 Nxf4 37. Nxf4 Qxf4 38. Nxd4 cxd4 $17) 33. Ng2 Nxb5 34. Qxb5 Kg7 35. Qb2 $2 (35. h3 Ne4 36. Kh2 Qf6 $15) 35... Qe4 $1 $17 36. Qc1 Qd4 37. h3 Ne4 38. Ne3 Nd2 39. Qg1 Qe4+ 40. Ng2 Qxc4 41. d6 Qd5 42. Qa1+ f6 43. Qb2 Qxd6 44. Qb7+ Kh6 45. Qxa7 Nf3 46. Ne3 f5 47. Qf7 Qd3 $2 (47... Nd4 48. Kg2 Qa6 $19 {was the clearest method.}) 48. Qe7 $1 Qd4 49. Nxf5+ $1 gxf5 50. Qe6+ Kg7 51. Qe7+ Kg6 52. Qe8+ Kf6 53. Qc6+ Ke7 54. Qxf3 Qa1+ 55. Kg2 Qxa2+ 56. Kg3 Qe6 57. Qb7+ Qd7 58. Qa6 Qe6 $2 ({Although Black will find it hard to cash in the point, this is his final mistake.} 58... Kf8 {was his only try.}) 59. Qa7+ Kd6 60. Qa6+ Kd5 61. Qd3+ Kc6 62. Qa6+ 1/2-1/2


