1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. e4 d6 5. f3 a6 6. Be3 c6 7. c5 b5 8. cxd6 (8. cxb6 Nbd7 (8... Qxb6 9. Qd2 O-O 10. Nge2 a5 11. g4 a4 12. Ng3 Qa5 $13 {Hauchard,A-Gurevich,M/Belfort 1998}) 9. Bd3 (9. Na4 Nxb6 10. Nxb6 Qxb6 11. Qd2 O-O 12. Ne2 a5 13. Nc3 Ba6 14. Bxa6 Qxa6 15. Qe2 Nd7 $11 {Gallego Eraso,F-Paunovic,D/Andorra 2003}) 9... Qxb6 10. Qd2 Rb8 11. b3 c5 12. Nge2 O-O 13. Na4 Qd8 14. O-O cxd4 15. Nxd4 Bb7 16. Rac1 d5 $13 {Nyback,T-Welling,G/Saint Vincent 2005}) 8... exd6 9. Bd3 (9. a4 $5 Bb7 10. Nh3 O-O 11. Be2 Nbd7 12. O-O Re8 13. Qd2 b4 14. Nd1 a5 15. Nhf2 c5 (15... Nf8 $5 16. Rc1 Ne6 17. Nd3 Nd7 $11) 16. d5 Ba6 17. Bxa6 Rxa6 18. Bg5 $14 {Korchnoi,V-Gheorghiu,F/Moscow 1971}) 9... O-O 10. Nge2 Nbd7 11. Qd2 (11. O-O c5 (11... Re8 12. Bf2 Bh6 13. b4 Nh5 14. a4 Nb6 $2 (14... bxa4 15. Qxa4 Bb7 $14) 15. d5 $1 cxd5 16. axb5 Nf6 17. bxa6 dxe4 18. Nxe4 $18 {Klebel,M-Wahls,M/Vienna 1991}) 12. Rc1 Bb7 13. d5 Ne5 14. a3 Nfd7 $11 {Alterman,B-Kreiman,B/New York 1997}) 11... c5 12. O-O cxd4 $5 13. Nxd4 Bb7 14. Rad1 d5 $1 15. exd5 (15. Bh6 Qb6 16. Bc2 Bxh6 17. Qxh6 Rfe8 $11) 15... Nxd5 16. Nxd5 Bxd5 17. Bb1 Nf6 18. Bh6 Qb6 $11 1/2-1/2


