1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6 3. g3 Bg7 4. Bg2 O-O 5. O-O d6 6. a4 a5 7. b3 Na6 8. Bb2 c6 9. Nbd2 Nc7 $6 ({This knight is misplaced on the c7-square. Black probably should pick-up one of the following options: a)} 9... d5 10. Ne5 (10. Re1 Bf5 11. Nh4 Bg4 12. h3 Be6 13. Nhf3 Qc8 14. Kh2 Qc7 15. c4 Nb4 16. Rc1 Qb6 17. Ne5 Rfd8 $11 {Stocek,J-Schmaltz,R/Germany 2000}) 10... Bf5 11. h3 Qc8 (11... Ne8 12. g4 Be6 13. f4 Nd6 14. e3 Nb4 15. c3 Na6 16. Nd3 b6 17. Qe2 c5 18. Ne5 $14 {Piskov,Y-Podzielny,K/Bonn 1995}) 12. Kh2 (12. g4 $5 Be6 13. Ba3 Qc7 14. c3 c5 15. e3) 12... Nd7 13. f4 Be6 14. g4 Nxe5 15. dxe5 Nc5 {½-½ D'Amore,C-Efimenko,Z/Plovdiv 2003}) ({b)} 9... Rb8 $6 10. e4 Bg4 11. h3 Bxf3 12. Qxf3 Nd7 13. Nc4 Qc7 14. Qe2 $16 {Almasi,I-Stanec,N/Oberwart 2000}) ({c)} 9... Bf5 10. Nh4 (10. h3 d5 11. Nh4 Be6 12. f4 Qc7 13. e3 c5 14. c3 $11 {Horn,P-Gallagher,J/Zuerich 1999}) 10... Be6 11. e4 $14) ({d)} 9... Bg4 10. Nc4 Bxf3 11. exf3 d5 12. Ne3 Ne8 13. f4 Nd6 14. h4 e6 15. h5 $14 {Nalbandian,T-Hug,W/Biel 1993}) 10. e4 Bg4 11. h3 Bxf3 12. Qxf3 Nd7 13. Rad1 ({Also good is} 13. Nc4 Na6 14. Qe2 Qc7 15. e5 $16 {Vandrey,W-Ryskin,A/Berlin 1993}) 13... e6 $6 (13... f5 14. Qe3 fxe4 15. Nxe4 Nf6 16. c4 $16) 14. Ba3 $1 Bxd4 (14... Ne8 15. Nc4 Qc7 16. e5 $18) 15. Bxd6 Ne5 16. Bxe5 Bxe5 17. Nc4 Qf6 18. Qxf6 Bxf6 19. Rd7 $2 $16 (19. Nb6 Rad8 20. Nd7 $18) 19... b5 20. axb5 Nxb5 $2 (20... cxb5 21. e5 Nd5 22. Bxd5 exd5 23. Nxa5 Bxe5 24. Rxd5 $16) 21. e5 $18 Bg7 22. Bxc6 Rab8 23. Ra1 Rfc8 24. Bxb5 Rxb5 25. f4 Bf8 26. Kf1 Bb4 27. Ke2 g5 28. fxg5 Bc3 29. Rf1 Bxe5 30. Rfxf7 a4 31. bxa4 Rbc5 32. Ne3 Bd4 33. Ng4 1-0


