1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 e5 4. Bc4 d6 5. d3 Be7 6. O-O Nf6 7. Ng5 O-O 8. f4 h6 (8... a6 $6 {½-½ Sveshnikov,E-Rashkovsky,N/Moscow 1973/[Erenburg] (36)}) (8... Bg4 9. Nf3 (9. Qd2 exf4 $146 (9... h6 {½-½ Smirin,I-Kosteniuk,A/Philadelphia 2003/[Erenburg] (36)}) 10. Qxf4 {½-½ Mueller,K-Boensch,U/TCh-AUT 2004/[Erenburg] (48)}) (9. Qe1 exf4 10. Bxf4 Nd4 11. e5 $5 (11. Qd2 Qd7 12. Be3 (12. h3 $5 Bh5 13. g4 Bg6 14. Nd5 b5 15. Bb3 Bd8 16. Rae1 Nxb3 17. axb3 Nxd5 18. exd5 Bf6 $15 {1/2-1/2 Ponomariov,R-Radjabov,T/XX SuperGM, Linares ESP 2003 (41)}) (12. a4 {½-½ Kramnik,V-Grischuk,A/Wijk aan Zee 2003/[Roiz,M] (20)}) 12... h6 {1-0 Kramnik,V-Degraeve,J/Senat 2003/[Erenburg] (30)} (12... a6 13. Bxd4 cxd4 14. Ne2 h6 15. Nf3 d5 16. exd5 Bxf3 17. Rxf3 Nxd5 18. Nxd4 {1/2-1/2 Nisipeanu,L-Van Wely,L/4th IECC, Istanbul TUR 2003 (18)}) 13. Nf3 Nxf3+ 14. gxf3 Be6 15. Kh1 Kh7 16. Bxe6 fxe6 $146 (16... Qxe6 17. Rae1 Qh3 18. Qg2 Qxg2+ 19. Kxg2 a6 20. f4 $14 {1-0 Kramnik,V-Degraeve,J/Final Coupe de France, Senat FRA 2003/[Erenburg] (30)}) 17. Qg2 {½-½ Bologan,V-Radjabov,T/Dortmund 2003/[Erenburg] (37)}) 11... dxe5 (11... Nxc2 12. exf6 (12. Qh4 {-see 12...xc2 variation.}) 12... Nxe1 13. fxe7 Qxe7 14. Raxe1 $16) 12. Bxe5 {½-½ Macieja,B-Gelfand,B/Plovdiv 2003/[Erenburg] (19)}) 9... exf4 (9... Nd4 10. f5 Nh5 11. Nd5 Bh4 12. Ne3 (12. Qd2 $5 Nxf3+ 13. gxf3 Bh3 14. Rd1 h6 15. Kh1 $14) 12... Nxf3+ 13. gxf3 Bh3 14. Ng2 Bg5 $132 {1/2-1/2 Ochoa de Echaguen,F-Remon,A/Havana 1983/MCL (28)}) 10. Bxf4 Nd4 (10... Ne5 11. Bxe5 dxe5 12. Qe1 $1 $14 {[%cal Yc4f7,Yf1f7]}) 11. Kh1 a6 (11... Qd7 {½-½ Gelfand,B-Leko,P/Budapest 2003/[Gofshtein,L] (29)}) (11... Nxf3 12. gxf3 Be6 13. Qe2 $1 (13. Rg1 d5 $11) 13... Nd7 (13... Re8 14. Rg1 d5 15. Qg2 g6 16. exd5 Nxd5 17. Nxd5 Bxd5 18. Bb5 $14) 14. Rg1 $14 {/=}) 12. Qd2 (12. a4 $5) 12... b5 {1-0 Anand,V-Van Wely,L/Monte Carlo 2003/[Erenburg] (39)}) (8... Nd4 {1-0 Lacasa Diaz,J-Vallejo Pons,F/Cordoba 1995/[Erenburg] (54)}) (8... exf4 9. Bxf4 Nd4 {0-1 Mnatsakanian,E-Yegiazarian,A/Yerevan 1994/[Erenburg] (27)} (9... Na5 10. Qd2 {0-1 Topalov,V-Van Wely,L/Wijk aan Zee 2003/[Erenburg] (37)})) 9. Nf3 (9. Nh3 $5 {1/2-1/2 Atlas,V-Nataf,I/Austria 2000/CBM 80/[Atlas,V] (43)}) 9... exf4 (9... Be6 $6 $146 {1-0 Kovalev,A-Votava,J/Passau 1995/[Erenburg] (53)}) 10. Bxf4 Be6 (10... Ng4 $6 $146 11. h3 $1 {1-0 Delchev,A-Fernandez Siles,L/Albacete 2003/[Erenburg] (20)}) 11. Nd5 (11. Qd2 Kh7 (11... d5 {½-½ De Firmian,N-Browne,W/Seattle 2003/[Erenburg] (18)}) (11... Bxc4 $6 12. dxc4 Re8 13. Rad1 Bf8 14. Rfe1 Re6 15. a3 Qa5 16. Qd3 Rae8 17. h3 a6 18. Re2 Nd7 19. Nd5 Qd8 20. Bg3 $14 {½-½ Nikolenko,O-Ikonnikov,V/Tula 2000 (50)}) 12. Rae1 {½-½ Eismont,O-Zagorskis,D/Berlin 1995/[Erenburg] (37)}) 11... Bxd5 (11... Qd7 12. Qd2 {0-1 Mitkov,N-Kurajica,B/Oberwart 1991/[Erenburg] (44)}) 12. exd5 (12. Bxd5 {0-1 Podlesnik,B-Sveshnikov,E/Ljubljana 2002/[Finkel,A] (53)}) 12... Na5 (12... Nb4 13. Bd2 $1 (13. Nh4 $2 Nfxd5) 13... Nbxd5 (13... Nfxd5 $2 14. a3 $16) (13... Nd7 $6 14. a3 Na6 15. Bxa6 bxa6 16. c4 Bf6 17. Rb1 $16) 14. Nh4 Nb6 (14... Nc7 {1-0 Macieja,B-Bobras,P/Warsaw 2002/[Postny] (46)}) 15. Nf5 d5 $2 (15... Nxc4 {1-0 Smirin,I-Avrukh,B/Tel Aviv 2002/[Avrukh,B] (33)}) 16. Qe1 $1 {1-0 Tiviakov,S-Ledger,S/Catalan Bay 2003/[Erenburg] (21)}) 13. Qe1 $146 {White's idea is to transfer the queen to the kingside, probably to g3.} (13. Qd2 $146 Nxc4 {½-½ Timofeev,A-Grebionkin,V/playchess.com 2003/[Erenburg (55)}) ({Much more principle is} 13. Nh4 b5 (13... Nxc4 {½-½ Kramnik,V-Leko,P/Linares 2003/[Meyer,CD] (35)}) (13... Qd7 $6 {1-0 Gallagher,J-Heidrich,M/Germany 2003/[Meyer,CD] (32)}) 14. Nf5 {1-0 Sutovsky,E-Smirin,I/ch-ISR, Tel Aviv ISR 2002/[Stohl] (24)}) 13... a6 $6 (13... Nxc4 $142 14. dxc4 Re8 15. Qg3 $6 (15. Kh1 $142 {-like in the game, but the pawns are located on a6 and a3.}) 15... Nh5 (15... Qd7 $5 16. Bxh6 $141 Nh5 17. Qf2 gxh6 18. Ne5 dxe5 19. Qxf7+ Kh8 20. Qxh5 Bg5 $17) 16. Qg4 Nxf4 17. Qxf4 Bf6 $11) 14. a3 $6 (14. Nh4 $142 Re8 (14... b5 15. Nf5 Re8 (15... bxc4 16. Bd2 $1 Re8 17. Bxa5 Qd7 18. Qg3 $18) 16. Qg3 Bf8 17. Nxh6+ Kh7 18. Nxf7 $18) 15. Nf5 Nh5 $1 (15... Bf8 16. Qg3 $16 Nh5 17. Nxh6+ Kh7 18. Qg4 Nxf4 19. Nxf7 Ne2+ 20. Kh1 $18 {[%cal Gg4h5]}) 16. Qf2 b5 17. Bb3 Nxf4 18. Qxf4 $14) 14... Nxc4 15. dxc4 Re8 {Black goes on a right plan. Better later, than never!} 16. Kh1 {White is waiting for black's f8, thus black will not be able to occupy a long diagonal immediately.} Bf8 17. Qg3 Ne4 {looks very logical.} (17... Nh5 18. Qg4 Nxf4 (18... Nf6 $5 19. Qf5 (19. Qh3 $5) 19... Qc8 20. Qd3) 19. Qxf4 $14 {[%cal Ga1e1]}) 18. Qg4 (18. Qh3 Qc8) 18... Qc8 $1 19. Qh5 $2 (19. Qxc8 Raxc8 20. Rae1 $11) 19... g6 20. Qh4 g5 21. Bxg5 hxg5 22. Nxg5 Nxg5 23. Qxg5+ Bg7 $17 24. Rf5 Qd8 25. Qh5 Qe7 26. Raf1 Rf8 27. h3 Rae8 28. R1f4 Qe1+ 29. Kh2 Re5 30. Rh4 Qxh4 31. Qxh4 Rxf5 32. Qe7 Be5+ 33. Kg1 b5 34. cxb5 axb5 35. c3 Rf4 36. Qg5+ 1/2-1/2


